0actually%20condemned%20Israel%20for%20assassinating%20two%20Hamas%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20appalled%20by%20the%20killing%20in%20Gaza%20of%20Sheikh%20Ahmed%20Yassin%2C%20spiritual%20leader%20of%20Hamas%2C%20yesterday%20in%20an%20Israeli%20missile%20strike%2C%E2%80%9D%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi-appalled-the-day-after%2Fcid%2F760615%5C%22%3E%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20March%202004%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20when%20Israel%20killed%20his%20successor%2C%20Abdel%20Aziz%20Al-Rantisi%2C%20India%20again%20censured%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20special%20meeting%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2004%2Fsc8063.doc.htm%5C%22%3Ein%20April%202004%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ambassador%20Vijay%20Nambiar%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%20killing%20of%20al-Rantisi%20was%20unjustified%20and%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20could%20not%20be%20condoned%20under%20any%20circumstances.%C2%A0Such%20action%2C%20following%20closely%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Sheikh%20Ahmed%20Yassin%2C%20could%20only%20lead%20to%20a%20further%20deterioration%20of%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20region%20and%20escalation%20of%20the%20cycle%20of%20violence%20and%20counter-violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20World%20Must%20Wake%20Up%20to%20Israel's%20Lies%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-world-must-wake-up-to-israels-lies%5C%22%3EThe%20World%20Must%20Wake%20Up%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Lies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20if%20India%2C%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20will%20shift%20from%20the%20past%20or%20maintain%20continuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20designated%20certain%20transnational%20groups%20as%20terrorist%20entities%20%E2%80%93%20including%20ISIS%20and%20Al-Qaida%20%E2%80%93%20this%20was%20done%20pursuant%20to%20listings%20by%20ISIL%20and%20Al-Qaida%20Sanctions%20Committee%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20pursuant%20to%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolution%201267.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Hamas%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20terrorist%20entity%20under%20the%20UN%20list%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20designation%20of%20Hamas%20as%20terrorists%20would%20be%20setting%20a%20new%20precedent%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20something%20the%20MEA%20might%20be%20unwilling%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20likely%20that%20India%20will%20continue%20with%20its%20dichotomous%20approach%2C%20invoking%20terror%20acts%20by%20Hamas%20in%20order%20to%20justify%20a%20diplomatic%20stand%20that%20is%20driven%20by%20political%20considerations%20but%20stopping%20short%20of%20designating%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20under%20Indian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20only%20terrorist%20groups%20directly%20impacting%20the%20subcontinent%20or%20transnational%20outfits%20recognised%20by%20the%20UN%20have%20been%20listed%20under%20section%2035%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20and%20that%20position%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArkoprabho%20Hazra%20works%20as%20a%20manager%20at%20Aakhya%20India%20and%20writes%20occasionally%20on%20matters%20related%20to%20Indian%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHe%20tweets%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%20%40ArkoprabhoH.%20%3Cem%3EViews%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700219157000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14000534%2F1600px-Prime_Minister_of_India_Narendra_Modi_at_an_informal_meeting_of_heads_of_state_and_government_of_the_BRICS_countries_Hamburg_2017.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fon-hamas-modi-government-wants-to-have-its-anti-terror-cake-and-eat-it-too%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22