ents.%3Cp%3EFrank%20Rumpenhorst%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Pew%20Center%20study%20found%20that%20one%20in%20five%20teens%20who%20have%20heard%20of%20ChatGPT%20have%20used%20it%20for%20schoolwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETeachers%20fear%20the%20huge%20popularity%20of%20the%20chatbot%20is%20fuelling%20a%20cheating%20epidemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20is%20exploring%20how%20to%20integrate%20ChatGPT%20even%20further%20into%20classrooms%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20takeover%20of%20the%20classroom%20is%20not%20slowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fabout-1-in-5-us-teens-whove-heard-of-chatgpt-have-used-it-for-schoolwork%2F%3Futm_source%3DAdaptiveMailer%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3D22-11-16%2520Teens%3A%2520AI%2520and%2520school%2520short%2520read%26org%3D982%26lvl%3D100%26ite%3D12931%26lea%3D2940954%26ctr%3D0%26par%3D1%26trk%3Da0DQm000000aoEPMAY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPew%20research%20center%20survey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20US%20teens%20aged%20between%2013%20and%2017%20has%20found%20that%20one%20in%20five%20students%20who%20have%20heard%20of%20the%20generative%20chatbot%20have%20used%20it%20to%20help%20with%20their%20schoolwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20two-thirds%20of%20US%20teenagers%20having%20heard%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20that%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20kids%20using%20OpenAI's%20chatbot%20to%20help%20write%20essays%20and%20solve%20math%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20will%20likely%20only%20add%20to%20concerns%20over%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20text-generators%20in%20schools.%20ChatGPT%20is%20so%20popular%20among%20students%20right%20now%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschool-is-back-chatgpt-mainly-tool-cheating-homework-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20traffic%20