C%20till%208%20am%20today%20(November%2017)...%207%20hours%20after%20returning%20from%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20I%20was%20going%20to%20the%20US%20from%2016-23%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20At%20immigration%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'LoC%20%3Cem%3Elaga%20hua%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20sir%20-%20EOW%20%3Cem%3Ese%20%3C%2Fem%3Echeck%20%3Cem%3Ekar%20ke%20batate%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(There%20is%20a%20LoC%2C%20sir...%20we%20will%20check%20with%20EoW%20and%20let%20you%20know)'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20I%20found%20it%20strange%20as%20(I)%20have%20travelled%20four%20times%20internationally%20since%20(the)%20FIR%20(was)%20filed%20in%20May%20-%20(there%20has)%20never%20been%20a%20problem...%20I%20had%20not%20even%20been%20summoned%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Flight%20left%20in%20meantime%20anyways%3B%20EoW%20folks%20directed%20Immigration%20to%20let%20us%20out%20so%20we%20can%20return%20home%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Today%20morning%2C%20EoW%20summon%20was%20home%20delivered%20-%20will%20cooperate%20as%20always.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHello%20!%20Hello%20!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKya%20chal%20raha%20hai%20India%20mein%20%3F%20Filhaal%20to%20Ashneer%20stopped%20at%20airport%20chal%20raha%20hai%20janab.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSo%20facts%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20I%20had%20not%20received%20any%20communication%20or%20summon%20from%20EOW%20since%20FIR%20in%20May%20till%208%20AM%20today%2017%20morning%20(7%20hours%20after%20returning%20from%20airport).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20I%20was%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FI0OHOXJd6F%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FI0OHOXJd6F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ashneer%20Grover%20(%40Ashneer_Grover)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshneer_Grover%2Fstatus%2F1725435360858321374%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Grover%2C%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20having%20quite%20a%20chuckle%20over%20the%20whole%20incident%2C%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20drama.%20LOC%3Cem%3E%20hatane%20ka%20process%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20-%20I%20am%20not%20a%20flight%20risk%20-%20easy%20to%20prove%20(No%20drama.%20There%20is%20a%20process%20to%20remove%20the%20LoC...%20I%20am%20not%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%20this%20is%20easy%20to%20prove).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBaaki%20aapko%20jo%20chhaapna%20hai%20chhaapo%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Picture%3Cem%3E%20chal%20rahi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20free%20%3Cem%3Emein%20%3C%2Fem%3E-%20%3Cem%3Emaze%20lo%3C%2Fem%3E!%20(Whatever%20else%20you%20want%20to%20print%2C%20print...%20the%20picture%20is%20playing%20for%20free%20-%20enjoy!)%26quot%3B%20the%20under-fire%20businessman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%2C%20who%20now%20runs%20CrickPe%2C%20a%20fantasy%20sports%20app%20-%20finished%20on%20a%20defiant%20note%3B%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBaaki%20premature%20obituaries%20bahut%20baari%20log%20likh%20chuke%20hai%20-%20'Jatt%20mareya%20tad%20maniye%20jad%20terami%20howe%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(Don't%20pronounce%20me%20dead%20till%2013%20days%20after%20you've%20burned%20me%20at%20the%20pyre!)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20fraud%20at%20BharatPe%20has%20uncovered%20unexplained%20payments%20allegedly%20made%20to%20HR%20firms%20by%20Mr%20Grover%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20other%20members%20of%20their%20family%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FBharatPe%2520Ex-CEO%2520Ashneer%2520Grover%2C%2520Family%2520Made%2520Fake%2520Multi-Crore%2520Invoices%3A%2520Sources%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBharatPe%20Ex-CEO%20Ashneer%20Grover%2C%20Family%20Made%20Fake%20Multi-Crore%20Invoices%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20allegedly%20used%20backdated%20invoices%20to%20move%20funds%20from%20BharatPe's%20accounts%20for%20pay