0his%20family%20that%20he%20was%20hooked%20to%20playing%20games%20on%20his%20phone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2F16-year-old-mumbai-boy-dies-by-suicide-after-father-takes-away-his-cellphone%2Farticleshow%2F105289053.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20on%20Paper%20Leaks%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Adani%2C%20and%20the%20Importance%20of%20Forgetting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17133446%2FPilot.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20the%20Rajasthan%20elections%20mere%20days%20away%2C%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Sachin%20Pilot%20has%20been%20actively%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20not%20just%20in%20Rajasthan%20but%20also%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20At%20Tonk%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3Cem%3Ecaught%20up%20with%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20seeing%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20comes%20to%20power%20every%2010%20years%2C%20but%20its%20vote%20share%20keeps%20decreasing.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20party%20won%20with%20a%20small%20margin%20of%200.5%25.%20Do%20you%20think%20the%20party%20will%20even%20win%20this%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20every%20election%20is%20different.%20Last%20time%2C%20we%20fought%20the%20elections%20with%20just%2021%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20we%20went%20from%2021%20to%20100%2C%20and%20this%20time%20we%20are%20in%20power%20and%20have%20a%20report%20card%20to%20show%20the%20public%20what%20we%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20373px)%2085vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20find%20an%20environment%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20also%20present%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana.%20The%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20any%20work%20as%20an%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20I%20believe%20people%20have%20seen%20their%20ten%20years%20of%20work%20in%20the%20country%20also%2C%20and%20shortcomings%20in%20it%20have%20also%20become%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20has%20to%20find%20a%20better%20option%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20youth%20like%20you%20very%20much%20but%20have%20been%20angry%20over%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20If%20we%20calculate%20the%20average%2C%20three%20papers%20have%20been%20leaked%20every%20year%20since%202019.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20agree%2C%20paper%20leaks%20are%20a%20big%20issue%20here%20in%20Rajasthan%3B%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20compromise%20with%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20play%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20youth.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20compromise%20on%20this%20issue.%20Paper%20leaks%20are%20a%20problem%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20that%20my%20party%20has%20listened%20to%20my%20concern%2C%20and%20the%20punishment%20for%20paper%20leaks%20in%20our%20state%20is%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20government%20cares%20for%20the%20students%3A%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20the%20first%20government%20in%20the%20state%20who%20has%20made%20a%20law%20on%20paper%20leaks%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20harshest%20punishment%20has%20been%20provided%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22At%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan's%20'Yogi'%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahant-baba-balaknath-rajasthan-election-yogi-adityanath%5C%22%3EAt%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Yogi%E2%80%99%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20spoke%20about%20the%20youth%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20one%20more%20issue%20that%20we%20have%20been%20seeing%20in%20Rajasthan.%20In%20Kota%2C%20we%20see%20thousands%20of%20students%20coming%20every%20year%20to%20prepare%20for%20%5Bthe%20JEE%20and%20NEET%5D.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20over%2025%20suicides.%20What%20is%20the%20solution%3F%20Because%20students%20from%20the%20entire%20country%20come%20to%20Kota.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20suicide%20incidents%20are%20increasing%20in%20Kota.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20social%20problem.%20Lakhs%20of%20children%20come%20to%20study%3B%20we%20are%20also%20providing%20counselling%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20is%20the%20solution%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20think%20about%20it%3B%20failure%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20looked%20down%20upon.%20These%20are%20societal%20issues%2C%20young%20people%20committing%20suicide%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20worst%20thing%20for%20any%20country%20or%20any%20society.%20I%20am%20very%20sad%20about%20these%20things%20coming%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20supremo%20Mayawati%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fbsp-will-contest-from-all-200-seats-in-rajasthan-says-party-leader%2Farticleshow%2F103182478.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%20her%20party%20will%20be%20contesting%20all%20200%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20BSP%20has%20influence%20over%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20votes.%20Do%20you%20think%20it%20can%20affect%20the%20Congress%3F%20As%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%202018%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20%5Bwhich%20went%20on%20to%20form%20the%20government%5D%20won%20more%20SC%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20parties%20contest%20elections%2C%20but%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20elections%20are%20held%20mainly%20between%20only%20two%20parties%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20These%20parties%20have%20been%20contesting%20before%20also%3B%20parties%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20might%20get%20one%20or%20two%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20main%20contest%20will%20always%20be%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20these%20regional%20parties%2C%20what%20is%20their%20situation%20in%20their%20own%20state%3F%20So%20I%20believe%20that%20people%20from%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20stand%20with%20the%20Congress%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-bjp-battle-bsp-influence-electoral-outcome%5C%22%3EAs%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20Battle%20for%20Rajasthan%2C%20Can%20BSP%20Influence%20Electoral%20Outcome%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20about%20Hanuman%20Beniwal%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20also%20contesting%20this%20%3Cem%3Evidhan%20sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20I%20told%20you%20%E2%80%93%20many%20parties%20contest%20elections%20here%2C%20but%20the%20competition%20is%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20only.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20also.%20These%20parties%20may%20get%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20the%20vote%20share%2C%20but%20I%20am%20telling%20you%2C%20for%20every%20society%2C%20whether%20urban%20or%20rural%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20a%20better%20place%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2013%2Frajasthan%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-election-bjp-win-biggest-ever-congress-loss-biggest-ever-220101-2013-12-07%5C%22%3ECongress%20experienced%20its%20worst%20defeat%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20party%20had%20only%2021%20MLAs%20left%20%E2%80%93%20after%20which%20the%20elections%20of%202018%20were%20imposed%20under%20your%20leadership.%20But%20why%20did%20the%20party%20still%20not%20make%20you%20the%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20is%20right%3B%20we%20were%2021%20only%2C%20and%20we%20struggled%20a%20lot%20to%20make%20it%20100%20in%20Rajasthan.%20We%20struggled%20for%20five%20years%2C%20on%20the%20street%20%E2%80%93%20we%20faced%20lathi%20charges%2C%20we%20went%20to%20jail%2C%20we%20staged%20protests%2C%20yatras%20and%20gheraos%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20after%20this%20that%20the%20people%20blessed%20us%20and%20put%20us%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20always%20say%20that%20governments%20are%20made%20by%20parties%2C%20but%20the%20reverse%20isn%E2%80%99t%20true.%20Our%20first%20priority%20is%20that%20the%20party%20organisation%20should%20remain%20strong.%20Then%2C%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20after%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20MLAs%2C%20it%20will%20be%20decided%20who%20should%20be%20given%20what%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20all%20have%20the%20same%20objective%3A%20seeing%20how%20we%20can%20form%20a%20strong%20Congress%20government%20here.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20stronger%20Congress%20when%20we%20form%20governments%20in%20different%20states%20of%20the%20country%3B%20hence%20the%20Rajasthan%20election%20is%20important%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20are%20going%20to%20vote%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%2010%20days%20%5Bfrom%20the%20date%20of%20the%20interview%5D%3B%20why%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20not%20campaigning%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20is%20here%20only%2C%20and%20he%20will%20be%20here%20till%20November%2023%3B%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20all%20have%20programmes%20here.%20Today%2C%20i.e.%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20November%2015%2C%20the%20election%20campaign%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20ended.%20You%20will%20meet%20everyone%20here%20till%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Emergence%20as%20Another%20Hindutva%20Laboratory%20Keeps%20BJP%20Afloat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-hindutva-laboratory-bjp-afloat%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Emergence%20as%20Another%20Hindutva%20Laboratory%20Keeps%20BJP%20Afloat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20your%20opinion%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20continuously%20raising%20in%20Rajasthan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20should%20be%20a%20top%20priority%20and%20should%20not%20be%20politicised.%20It%20is%20mandatory%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20for%20any%20incident%20that%20happens%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20try%20to%20suppress%20the%20incidents.%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20UP%20or%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%A6%20everyone%20knows%20that%20there%20are%20things%20happening%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20which%20are%20exposed%20later.%20Here%2C%20we%20do%20not%20try%20to%20suppress%20the%20facts%20around%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20priority%20here%20is%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20whatever%20incident%20happens%2C%20how%20quickly%20we%20take%20action%20on%20it%20and%20how%20quickly%20we%20get%20the%20culprit%20punished%20is%20our%20priority.%20We%20have%20done%20strong%20work%20in%20that%20direction%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20always%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20issues%20to%20raise%2C%20do%20they%3F%20Cylinder%20prices%20are%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20and%20so%20are%20those%20of%20petrol%20and%20diesel.%20How%20high%20is%20unemployment%3F%20Can%20anyone%20imagine%20by%20how%20much%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20has%20increased%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20government%20has%20sold%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20airports%2C%20railways%2C%20ports%2C%20power%20plants%20and%20mines%20at%20throwaway%20prices.%20The%20incomes%20of%20farmers%20have%20not%20even%20doubled%3B%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20even%20have%20its%20report%20card%20to%20show%2C%20so%20they%20are%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20others.%20People%20will%20reply%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20giving%20seven%20guarantees%20in%20Rajasthan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(1)%20an%20annual%20honorarium%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20family%2C%20(2)%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20to%201.05%20crore%20families%2C%20(3)%20the%20purchase%20of%20dung%20from%20cattle%20rearers%20at%20Rs%202%20per%20kg%2C%20(4)%20a%20law%20for%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20for%20government%20employees%2C%20(5)%20a%20laptop%20or%20tablet%20to%20students%20taking%20admission%20in%20government%20colleges%2C%20(6)%20insurance%20cover%20up%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20per%20family%20to%20compensate%20for%20losses%20due%20to%20natural%20calamities%20and%20(7)%20school%20education%20in%20the%20English%20medium.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20where%20will%20the%20party%20bring%20the%20funds%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww