r%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let%20us%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20and%20then%20we%20will%20take%20this%20decision.%20We%20will%20seek%20advice%20from%20legislators%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20our%20old%20tradition%20for%20decades%20that%20we%20first%20form%20the%20government%20and%20then%20decide%20who%20will%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20considering%20the%20views%20of%20our%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20members%20and%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20MLAs%20or%20even%20the%20decision%20of%20senior%20leaders.%20We%20have%20seen%20in%20September%202022%20how%20MLAs%20have%20different%20opinions%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leaders%20about%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20president%20Mr%20Kharge%20told%20me%20to%20forgive%2C%20forget%20and%20move%20forward%2C%20and%20asked%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20repeating%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20look%20ahead%2C%20and%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20party%20is%20to%20first%20win%20the%20election%20and%20then%20make%20the%20decision%20about%20who%20will%20get%20what.%20Chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20also%20apologised%20for%20the%20incident%20you%20are%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20text%20of%20this%20interview%20was%20lightly%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700216543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17133446%2FPilot.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-interview-2023-rajasthan-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20to%20The%20Wire%2C%20the%20former%20Rajasthan%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20also%20spoke%20on%20women's%20safety%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20prudent%20fiscal%20management.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-interview-2023-rajasthan-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20clamps%20down%20on%20migrants%20with%20criminal%20convictions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700216541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105290074%2Cimgsize-1137810.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralia-clamps-down-on-migrants-with-criminal-convictions%2Farticleshow%2F105289969.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105289969.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAustralia%20has%20passed%20legislation%20allowing%20for%20home%20curfews%20and%20ankle%20bracelets%20to%20be%20imposed%20on%20migrants%20with%20criminal%20convictions.%20The%20law%20was%20rushed%20through%20after%20a%20court%20ruling%20forced%20the%20release%20of%20scores%20of%20detainees%20from%20detention%20centers.%20The%20legislation%20imposes%20penalties%20of%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20breaching%20the%20monitoring%20and%20curfew%20conditions.%20Civil%20rights%20groups%20have%20criticized%20the%20law%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20unfairly%20targets%20migrants%20and%20refugees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralia-clamps-down-on-migrants-with-criminal-convictions%2Farticleshow%2F105289969.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralia-clamps-down-on-migrants-with-criminal-convictions%2Famp_articleshow%2F105289969.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%