Garba.%20%26quot%3BI%20recently%20saw%20a%20video%20in%20which%20I%20was%20seen%20singing%20a%20Garba%20song.%20There%20are%20many%20other%20such%20videos%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20journalists%20at%20BJP's%20Diwali%20Milan%20programme%20at%20the%20party's%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20asked%20the%20media%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20times%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20technology%20should%20be%20used%20responsibly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20remarks%20come%20after%20deepfake%20videos%20-%C2%A0with%20morphed%20faces%20of%20actor%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Kajol%20-%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%2C%20evoking%20huge%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20sparked%20concerns%20over%20the%20ramifications%20of%20such%20tinkering%2C%20especially%20for%20public%20figures%2C%20who%20may%20get%20in%20trouble%20over%20visuals%20their%20faces%20are%20doctored%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20voices%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20including%20legendary%20actor%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20flagged%20the%20matter%20and%20called%20for%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20last%20week%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20underlining%20the%20legal%20provisions%20that%20cover%20such%20deepfakes%20and%20the%20penalties%20their%20creation%20and%20circulation%20may%20attract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blegal%20obligation%26quot%3B%20for%20online%20platforms%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation.%26quot%3BRemove%20any%20such%20content%20when%20reported%20within%2036%20hours%20of%20such%20reporting%20and%20ensure%20expeditious%20action%2C%20well%20within%20the%20timeframes%20stipulated%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%202021%2C%20and%20disable%20access%20to%20the%20content%20or%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20the%20minister%20added%2C%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20trust%20for%20Indians%20in%20the%20digital%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20said%20that%20creation%20and%20circulation%20of%20deepfakes%20carry%20strong%20penalty%20-%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20fine%20and%20three%20years%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700214960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2F1cvsauj_pm-modi-twitter_625x300_15_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20several%20deepfake%20videos%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20flagged%20the%20misuse%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20creating%20such%20videos%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20concern.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%203%20States...%26quot%3B%3A%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20Prediction%20For%20BJP%20in%20Assembly%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20in%20the%20US%20attending%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%2C%20but%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20back%20home.%20He%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%20on%20the%20elections%20and%20what%20the%20BJP%20has%20so%20far%20determined%20the%20results%20would%20be%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20he%20is%20confident%20the%20party%20will%20see%20a%20landslide%20win%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Rajasthan%2C%20while%20the%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20ahead%20in%20Chhattisgarh%26quot%3B%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%26quot%3Bwill%20return%20to%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20and%20analysts%20have%20predicted%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20lose%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20while%20Mizoram%20is%20unclear%20and%20the%20battle%20in%20Telangana%20is%20mainly%20between%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20these%20predictions%20as%20not%20reflecting%20the%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20clear%20what%20we%20see%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20TV%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20leads%20me%20to%20believe%20the%20tide%20has%20turned%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20we%20are%20clearly%20ahead%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20even%20before%20I%20left%20India%2C%20was%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20extensively.%20Rajasthan%20is%20looking%20to%20be%20a%20one-sided%20affair%3B%20we%20are%20doing%20extremely%20well%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhatisgarh%20are%20poised%20to%20give%20BJP%20victories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20he%20will%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20Telangana%20situation%20after%20he%20returns%20to%20India.%20%26quot%3BTelangana...%20voting%20is%20on%20November%2030.%20I%20have%20had%20only%20two%20visits%20to%20Telangana%20before%20coming%20here.%20Once%20am%20back%20and%20see%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20I%20will%20get%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20in%20at%20least%20three%20states%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20where%20he%20had%20extensively%20campianed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tesla%20and%20EVs%20in%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20his%20US%20visit%20was%20primarily%20for%20meeting%20the%20Tesla%20team%2C%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20whom%20are%20Indians%20who%20have%20done%20us%20proud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20wants%20to%20discuss%20Tesla's%20plans%20about%20elements%20from%20India%20in%20their%20supply%20chain%2C%20especially%20after%20Tesla%20doubled%20their%20imports%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20adopting%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%20very%20fast.%20Nearly%2040%20per%20cent%20two-wheelers%20are%20EVs%20now.%20For%20commercial%20buses%20and%20cabs%2C%20it's%20a%20no-brainer%20to%20use%20EVs%3B%20it's%20much%20more%20economical%20and%20eco-friendly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20private%20vehicles%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20the%20battery%20costs%20are%20a%20deterrent%20but%20will%20hopefully%20see%20a%20rapid%20price%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20the%20fastest%20growth%20of%20EVs%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20in%20India.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20bought%20a%20lot%20of%20EVs%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20on%20the%20roads%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20also%20met%20US%20leaders%20including%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20the%20APEC%20summit.%20He%20said%20India%20has%2