%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20political%20angle%20to%20this%20incident.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20enmity.%20Police%20parties%20have%20been%20dispatched%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgKtPGe3za0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgKtPGe3za0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1725441127946621280%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI's%20killing%20has%20sparked%20a%20predictable%20political%20spat%20and%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20outwitted%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20election%2C%20has%20come%20under%20combined%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa%20called%20the%20police%20officer's%20killing%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20disturbing%26quot%3B%20and%20lashed%20out%20at%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20whom%20he%20called%20%26quot%3B(Arvind)%20Kejriwal's%20driver%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20alarming%20to%20see%20so%20many%20murders%20and%20killings%20happening%20in%20Punjab.%20Bhagwant%20Mannji%2C%20Punjab%20entrusted%20(you%20to%20work%20for)%20responsible%20governance%2C%20not%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20Kejriwal's%20driver%3B%20compromising%20Punjab's%20interests%20for%20Kejriwal's%20agenda%20is%20not%20what%20the%20people%20voted%20for!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkali%20Dal%20leader%20Bikram%20Singh%20Majithia%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20react%2C%20also%20held%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20accountable%20for%20the%20cop's%20death%20and%20declared%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%26quot%3Bshame%20on%20you%20(Mr%20Mann)...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20situation%20in%20Punjab...%20ASI%20Saroop%20Singh...%20shot%20dead%20by%20unknown%20assailants%20this%20morning%20when%20he%20was%20going%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20as%20part%20of%20his%20duty...%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20insisted%20on%20showing%20his%20enthusiasm%20by%20holding%20an%20event%20first%20at%20PAP%20Ground%20Jalandhar%2C%20then%20PAU%20Ludhiana...%20while%20murders%2C%20extortions%2C%20robberies%20(take%20place)%20in%20Punjab.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDay%20in%20and%20day%20out%20looting%20has%20become%20a%20daily%20task...%20God%20is%20the%20protector%20of%20Punjab%20now...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress'%20youth%20wing%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Youth%20Congress%20shared%20a%20video%20clip%20from%20a%20local%20channel%20and%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BMurder%20of%20ASI!%20If%20those%20who%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Punjab%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20common%20people%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700212500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fsk16p2ko_punjab-police-officer-saroop-singh-shot-dead_625x300_17_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-cop-found-dead-under-mysterious-circumstances-in-amritsar-4581950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20senior%20police%20officer%20-%20Assistant%20Sub%20Inspector%20Saroop%20Singh%20-%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Punjab's%20Amritsar%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20and%20his%20death%20triggered%20an%20immediate%20political%20row.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-cop-found-dead-under-mysterious-circumstances-in-amritsar-4581950%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-cop-found-dead-under-mysterious-circumstances-in-amritsar-4581950%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-cop-found-dead-under-mysterious-circumstances-in-amritsar-4581950%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20Jinping%20offers%20more%20investment%20in%20South%20China%20Sea%20claimant%20Brunei%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700212416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105287617%2Cimgsize-18692.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-offers-more-investment-in-south-china-sea-claimant-brunei%2Farticleshow%2F105287530.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105287530.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20offered%20to%20increase%20its%20purchases%20of%20goods%20from%20Brunei%20and%20promote%20investment%20in%20the%20country%2C%20focusing%20on%20economic%20ties%20rather%20than%20territorial%20disputes%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20expressed%20China's%20willingness%20to%20expand%20cooperation%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20food%20security%20and%20joint%20maritime%20development.%20Brunei%2C%20which%20has%20a%20claim%20to%20part%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20has%20prioritized%20trade%20relations%20with%20China%20as%20it%20diversifies%20its%20economy.%20China%20is%20one%20of%20Brunei's%20major%20foreign%20investors%2C%20with%20significant%20investments%20in%20the%20oil%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-offers-more-investment-in-south-china-sea-claimant-brunei%2Farticleshow%2F105287530.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-offers-more-investment-in-south-china-sea-claimant-brunei%2Famp_articleshow%2F105287530.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-offers-more-investment-in-south-china-sea-claimant-brunei%2Famp_articleshow%2F105287530.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Bangladesh%20Looks%20For%20India's%20Help%20To%20Secure%20Mujib%20Ur%20Rahman's%20Killers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20likely%20to%20step%20up%20heat%20on%20two%20%26quot%3Bself-confessed%20killers%26quot%3B%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20and%20ensure%20their%20extradition%20to%20Dhaka%20soon%20after%20results%20are%20declared%20for%20the%20national%20election%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20theory%2C%20claim%20diplomatic%20sources%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20will%20work%20if%20the%20ruling%20Awami%20League%20returns%20to%20power%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20chances%20of%20which%20are%20extremely%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20process%20is%20going%20to%20be%20tough%2C%20it%20is%20all%20about%20some%20top-level%20political%20manoeuvring%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20where%20the%20killers%20are%20holed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20the%20US%20and%20Canadian%20laws%20permit%20people%20to%20be%20extradited%20to%20their%20home%20country%20if%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20face%20the%20death%20sentence%3F%20What%20is%20important%20is%20that%20the%20ongoing%20controversy%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20has%20given%20Dhaka%20the%20opportunity%20to%20remind%20the%20world%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wanted%20men%20in%20Bangladesh%20has%20eluded%20justice%20till%20now.%20And%20that%20they%20must%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20New%20Delhi%20could%20step%20in%20to%20help%20Dhaka.%20It%20has%20happened%20before%20and%20there%20are%20high%20chances%20it%20could%20happen%20again%20and%20New%20Delhi%20could%20put%20the%20heat%20on%20both%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20Bangladesh.%20It%20needs%20a%20mention%20here%20that%20a%20covert%2C%20joint%20operation%20between%20intelligence%20officers%20of%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Abdul%20Mazed%2C%20a%20former%20captain%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20army%20and%20one%20of%20the%20fugitives%20wanted%20for%20the%201975%20assassination%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman.%20Mazed%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%2C%202020%20from%20Mirpur%2C%20an%20industrial%20town%20close%20to%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20cognoscenti%20in%20the%20Delhi%20say%20covert%20operations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20will%20be%20on%20the%20rise.%20India%20will%20need%20help%20from%20its%20neighbour%20to%20flush%20out%20insurgent%20leaders%20in%20north-eastern%20states%20who%20often%20cross%20over%20to%20Bangladesh%20to%20escape%20the%20Indian%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20the%20million-dollar%20question%20is%20will%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20now%20bite%20the%20silver%20bullet%3F%20New%20representations%20-%20it%20is%20reliably%20learnt%20-%20will%20be%20made%20to%20the%20US%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20Attorney%20General%20Merrick%20B.%20Garland%20and%20Arif%20Virani%2C%20the%20law%20minister%20of%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20a%20big%20diplomatic%20tussle%20between%20Dhaka%2C%20Washington%20and%20Ottawa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20coup%20against%20Mujib%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assassination%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20and%20members%20of%20his%20family%20in%20a%20coup%20at%20their%20Dhanmondi%20bungalow%20on%20August%2015%2C%201975%20left%20the%20world%20shaken.%20Rehmani's%20two%20daughters%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20and%20Sheikh%20Rehana%2C%20were%20travelling%20abroad%20and%20were%20in%20Germany%2C%20hence%2C%20escaped.%20The%20coup%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20coterie%20of%20middle-level%20Army%20officers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewspaper%20reports%20in%20Dhaka%20say%20four%20groups%20of%20soldiers%20led%20by%20the%20coup%20plotters%20entered%20Dhaka%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20August%2015%2C%201975.%20The%20first%20group%20entered%20Sheikh%20Mujib's%20house%20and%20killed%20him%20after%20an%20argument%20and%20then%20went%20on%20to%20slaughter%20all%20members%20of%20the%20family%20as%20well%20as%20personal%20staff%20present%2C%20including%20a%20pregnant%20daughter-in-law%20of%20the%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20groups%20took%20over%20the%20radio%20station%2C%20key%20government%20buildings%20and%20disarmed%20security%20forces%20stationed%20at%20Savar%20in%20the%20city.%20Four%20Awami%20League%20leaders%20-%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bangladesh%20Tajuddin%20Ahmed%2C%20another%20former%20PM%20Mansur%20Ali%2C%20a%20former%20Vice%20President%20Syed%20Nazrul%20Islam%20and%20former%20home%20minister%20AHM%20Qamaruzzaman%20-%20were%20also%20arrested%20and%20incarcerated%20in%20Dhaka%20jail%2C%20and%20later%20murdered%20in%20prison.%20Bangladesh%20marks%20August%2015%20as%20a%20national%20day%20of%20mourning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20getting%20the%20fugitives%20from%20abroad%20will%20be%20a%20tough%20call%2C%20especially%20when%20Bangladesh%20supremo%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20would%20not%20bypass%20the%20legal%20route%20to%20adopt%20covert%20operations.%20Highly%20placed%20sources%20in%20Dhaka%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20some%20silent%2C%20diplomatic%20missions%20were%20sent%20to%20flush%20out%20these%20assassins%20but%20the%20moves%20did%20not%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20case%20of%20Aziz%20Pasha.%20When%20the%20mission%20from%20Dhaka%20reached%20Harare%2C%20the%20then%20president%20Robert%20Mugabe%20demanded%20a%20whopping%20%2410%20million%20to%20hand%20over%20Pasha.%20The%20cash%2C%20it%20is%20reliably%20learnt%2C%20was%20sought%20in%20a%20charity%20account%20in%20Senegal%20run%20by%20Mugabe's%20daughter.%20The%20effort%20did%20not%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20top%20Mossad%20officials%20flew%20to%20Dhaka%20to%20offer%20their%20help%20to%20extradite%20the%20assassins.%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20did%20not%20agree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETougher%20extradition%20process%20in%20US%2C%20Canada%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-eight%20long%20years%20have%20passed%20and%20the%20extradition%20process%20has%20become%20tough%2C%20sorry%20tougher.%20The%20two%20fugitive%20army%20officers%20have%20strong%20legal%20immunity.%20One%20is%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Canada%20and%20they%20cannot%20be%20extradited%20only%20because%20of%20political%20pressure.%20But%20top%20ministers%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20feel%20the%20two%20fugitive%20army%20officers%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20would%20eventually%20be%20brought%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%20Minister%20Anisul%20Huq%20was%20recently%20quoted%20in%20an%20interview%20saying%20that%20his%20country%20was%20negotiating%20a%20return%20of%20two%20killers%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20-%20Rashed%20Chowdhury%20from%20the%20US%20and%20SHBM%20Noor%20Chowdhury%20from%20Canada.%20Huq%20did%20not%20elaborate%20as%20to%20what%20were%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20negotiations%20set%20by%20Dhaka.%20There%20is%20another%20one%2C%20Major%20Shariful%20Haque%20Dalim%2C%20(a%20principal%20plotter%20behind%20the%20killing)%20who%20shuttles%20between%20Islamabad%20and%20Nairobi%20and%20is%20involved%20in%20some%20trading%20business%20in%20Kenya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20sources%20in%20Delhi%20say%20the%20process%20is%20tougher%20because%20Canada%20has%20laws%20which%20do%20not%20permit%20a%20person%20facing%20a%20death%20sentence%20at%20home%20to%20be%20extradited.%20And%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20process%20of%20extradition%20is%20stuck%20in%20a%20legal%20process%20that%20has%20continued%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20These%20are%20serious%20hurdles%20and%20can%20be%20ironed%20out%20through%20diplomatic%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20enough%20evidence%20available%20and%20their%20crime%20has%20been%20conclusively%20proven.%20But%20the%20countries%20where%20these%20three%20fugitives%20are%20stationed%20will%20not%20hand%20over%20these%20men%20unless%20there%20is%20some%20serious%2C%20global%20pressure.%20And%20then%20there%20are%20these%20serious%20legal%20hassles%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Prof.%20Veena%20Sikri%2C%20former%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20legal%20option%20is%20open%2C%20it%20is%20a%20long-drawn%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Prof.%20Sikri%2C%20now%20representing%20the%20Ford%20Foundation%20endowed%20chair%2C%20Bangladesh%20Studies%20Programme%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaka%20has%20had%20some%20success%20with%20the%20killers%20of%20Mujib%20and%20his%20family.%20Abdul%20Majed%2C%20a%20former%20captain%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20army%20and%20one%20of%20the%20killers%2C%20was%20hanged%20after%20being%20brought%20back%20from%20abroad.%20Ten%20years%20before%20that%2C%20five%20other%20convicts%20--%20Syed%20Farooq%20Rahman%2C%20Sultan%20Shahriar%20Rashid%20Khan%2C%20Bazlul%20Huda%2C%20AKM%20Mohiuddin%20Ahmed%20and%20Mohiuddin%20Ahmed%20--%20were%20executed%20in%20January%202010%2C%20while%20a%20fifth%20Aziz%20Pasha%20died%20in%20Zimbabwe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrangely%2C%20the%20August%2015%2C%201975%20assassinations%20remain%20unresolved%20till%20date.%20On%20paper%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20the%20killers%20simply%20implemented%20a%20long-hatched%20conspiracy%20but%20the%20kingpins%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20have%20so%20far%20remained%20unknown%20to%20the%20common%20public.%20In%20total%2C%2019%20people%20lay%20dead%2C%20including%20Mujib%20and%20his%20wife.%20Such%20a%20killing-spree%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20world%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killers%20were%20free%20from%20remorse%2C%20as%20they%20confessed%20to%20killing%20in%20a%20TV%20interview%20(ITV%2C%20London)%20in%201976.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fsupplements%2Fnational-mourning-day-2022%2Fnews%2Fwhat-was-behind-the-brutal-killing-3095296%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Daily%20Star%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Dhaka%20said%20Colonel%20Rashid%20had%20the%20audacity%20to%20be%20on%20record%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%20I%20have%20killed%20Sheikh%20Mujib.%20Dare%20you%20put%20me%20on%20trial%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20the%20following%3A%20%26quot%3BIncidentally%2C%20it%20may%20be%20mentioned%20that%20a%20blind%20cleric%20popularly%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Eandha%20huzur%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20residing%20in%20Hali%20Shohor%20of%20Chattogram%2C%20aided%20and%20abetted%20this%20crime%20by%20teaching%20Rashid%20and%20his%20wife%20Zubaida%20Rashid%20the%20Quranic%20verses%20to%20facilitate%20the%20killing%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujib.%20(Anthony%20Mascarenhas%2C%20%3Cem%3EBangladesh%3A%20Legacy%20of%20Blood%3C%2Fem%3E).%20This%20cleric%20cannot%20escape%20his%20role%20in%20perpetuating%20the%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESHMB%20Nur%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20convicted%20killer%20of%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20has%20claimed%20innocence%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20innocent.%20I%20did%20not%20assassinate%20the%20then%20president%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Nur%20Chowdhury%2C%20now%20in%20Canada%2C%20said%20in%20a%20feature%20interview%20aired%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(CBC)%20some%20years%20ago.%20Nur%20told%20the%20CBC%20interview%20that%20he%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20a%20Canadian%20court%20so%20that%20he%20is%20not%20extradited.%20Toronto-based%20Noor%20Chowdhury%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20refugee%20protection%20in%20Canada%20and%20is%20currently%20facing%20a%20deportation%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20November%2019%2C%202009%20upheld%20a%20High%20Court%20verdict%20that%20affirmed%20the%20trial%20court%20judgement%2C%20which%20sentenced%20Noor%2C%20along%20with%2011%20others%2C%20to%20death.%20The%20court%20also%20convicted%20Noor%20as%20the%20lone%20shooter%20who%20killed%20Bangabandhu.%20Noor%2C%20a%20former%20lieutenant%20colonel%20of%20Bangladesh%20army%2C%20has%20been%20absconding%20since%20the%20day%20the%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20October%202%2C%201996%20for%20assassinating%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20reliably%20learnt%20that%20Noor%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20Canadian%20citizenship%20and%20has%20recently%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20a%20Canadian%20court%20not%20to%20deport%20him%20to%20Bangladesh.%20In%20the%20petition%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20be%20executed%20if%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20extradite%20him.%20Dhaka%20hopes%20the%20petition%20will%20be%20rejected%2C%20Bangladesh%20is%20banking%20on%20Canadian%20law%20which%20is%20against%20the%20refuge-seekers%20who%20ask%20for%20shelter%20after%20committing%20atrocious%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ELondon%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20commented%20on%20August%2016%2C%201975%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20is%20killed%20so%20tragically%2C%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20emerge%20Bangladesh%20as%20a%20free%20country.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Bangladesh%20Observer%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20same%20date%2C%20wrote%20as%20the%20first%20sentence%20of%20its%20editorial%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20killing%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20was%20a%20historic%20necessity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20historical%20perspectives%20have%20no%20space%20in%20Bangladesh%20now%2C%20the%20killers%20must%20return%2C%20they%20must%20be%20repatriated%20from%20their%20places%20of%20hiding%2C%20say%20top%20government%20officials%20and%20intellectuals%20in%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20course%20to%20be%20decided%20after%20elections%20next%20year%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20diplomatic%20pressure%20needs%20to%20be%20exerted%20on%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States.%20Diplomats%20from%20Bangladesh%20need%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20Kenya%20to%20find%20the%20fugitive%20former%20army%20official%20and%20ensure%20his%20repatriation%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Zayadul%20Ahsan%20Pintu%2C%20top%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EDBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Bangladesh%20news%20channel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20killers%20wanted%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20Bangabandhu%20family%20and%20the%20upper%20echelon%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20leadership.%20The%20killers%20wanted%20to%20nullify%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Liberation%20War%20and%20retrieve%20the%20Pakistani%20ethos.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20needs%20to%20be%20built%20to%20get%20the%20killers%20back.%20It%20is%20a%20tough%20call%2C%20very%20tough%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ahsan%20Pintu.%20Some%20in%20Dhaka%20say%20Bangladesh%20should%20have%20set%20up%20a%20high-powered%20commission%20to%20look%20into%20the%20conspiracy%2C%20conspirators%2C%20(both%20home%20and%20foreign)%2C%20the%20killing%20and%20killers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPadma%20Shri%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20(Retd)%20Qazi%20Sajjad%20Ali%20Zahir%2C%20a%20highly%20decorated%20officer%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20Army%2C%20recently%20told%20a%20news%20channel%20that%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government%20has%20made%20all%20the%20efforts%3A%20through%20requests%2C%20diplomatic%20channels%20and%20meetings%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20%26quot%3BBut%20all%20our%20requests%20evoked%20the%20same%20reply%20from%20Canada.%20Chowdhury%20will%20receive%20capital%20punishment%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20called%20capital%20punishment%20in%20Canadian%20courts.%20Is%20it%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20for%20justice%2C%20when%20the%20killers%20themselves%20have%20admitted%20to%20their%20crime%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Lt%20Col%20(Retd)%20Zahir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20on%20the%20elections%20in%20Bangladesh%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shantanu%20Guha%20Ray%20is%20the%20Asia%20Editor%20of%20Central%20European%20News%2C%20UK.%20His%20book%20on%20the%20Indian%20coal%20market%2C%20Black%20Harvest%2C%20will%20hit%20the%20stands%20soon.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700212320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Ff71gm4k4_sheilkh-mujibur-rahman-fb-650_625x300_07_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-looks-for-indias-help-to-secure-ex-president-sheikh-mujibur-rahmans-killers-4582041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20is%20likely%20to%20step%20up%20heat%20on%20two%20%26quot%3Bself-confessed%20killers%26quot%3B%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20and%20ensure%20their%20extradition%20to%20Dhaka%20soon%20after%20results%20are%20declared%20for%20the%20national%20election%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-looks-for-indias-help-to-secure-ex-president-sheikh-mujibur-rahmans-killers-4582041%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-looks-for-indias-help-to-secure-ex-president-sheikh-mujibur-rahmans-killers-4582041%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-looks-for-indias-help-to-secure-ex-president-sheikh-mujibur-rahmans-killers-4582041%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emraan%20Hashmi%20on%20the%20controversial%20KWK%20episode%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700212316000%