ia%20on%20November%2015%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557074636d588dc55d22484%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221431%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20(R)%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20walk%20together%20after%20a%20meeting%20during%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20Leaders'%20week%20in%20Woodside%2C%20California%20on%20November%2015%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it's%20willing%20to%20help%20the%20US%20crack%20down%20on%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20says%20China%20is%20a%20main%20source%20of%20materials%20for%20fentanyl%20that%20later%20ends%20up%20in%20America.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20experts%20are%20skeptical%20that%20the%20deal%2C%20scant%20on%20details%2C%20will%20result%20in%20change%20on%20US%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20agreed%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20fentanyl%20production%2C%20a%20move%20the%20US%20has%20championed%20as%20a%20key%20step%20toward%20subduing%20its%20opiate%20epidemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%2C%20which%20both%20leaders%20settled%20at%20the%20Asian-Pacific%20Economic%20Committee%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20would%20see%20Beijing%20assist%20Washington%20by%20regulating%20fentanyl%20precursors%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dea.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-03%2FDEA_GOV_DIR-008-20%2520Fentanyl%2520Flow%2520in%2520the%2520United%2520States_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrug%20Enforcement%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20warned%20in%20recent%20years%20that%20China%20is%20a%20primary%20source%20for%20key%20ingredients%20in%20fentanyl.%20Those%20ingredients%20are%20shipped%20to%20places%20where%20the%20drug%20is%20created%20for%20illegal%20consumption%20in%20the%20US%2C%20per%20the%20DEA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20few%20details%20were%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20is%20more%20of%20a%20positive%20sign%20in%20diplomacy%20and%20less%20of%20a%20concrete%20hope%20that%20Americans%20can%20start%20seeing%20fentanyl%20vanish%20from%20city%20streets%2C%20experts%20on%20US-China%20relations%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20success%20is%20defined%20by%20the%20disappearance%20of%20illicit%20fentanyl%20and%20related%20opioids%20in%20US%20society%2C%20then%20quite%20probably%2C%20any%20such%20deal%20with%20any%20country%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20judged%20as%20ineffective%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zha%20Daojiong%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20international%20political%20economy%20at%20Peking%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChina's%20role%20in%20a%20massive%20fentanyl%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20and%20Xi%20both%20face%20a%20behemoth%20challenge%3A%20a%20highly%20lucrative%20international%20drug%20trade%20that%20often%20teeters%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20what's%20legal%20and%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20precursors%20to%20fentanyl%2C%20originally%20created%20as%20a%20painkiller%2C%20are%20legal%20to%20produce%20and%20export%20in%20China%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20Beijing%20will%20crack%20down%20on%20the%20local%20pharma%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20industry%20too%20vast%20and%20fragmented%20for%20Chinese%20authorities%20to%20easily%20identify%20and%20control%20chemicals%20that%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20fentanyl%2C%20said%20Liu%20Zongyuan%2C%20the%20Maurice%20R.%20Greenberg%20fellow%20for%20China%20studies%20at%20the%20Council%20of%20Foreign%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Beijing%20were%20to%20impose%20the%20right%20limits%20on%20the%20right%20parties%2C%20cartels%20can%20start%20looking%20elsewhere%20for%20materials%2C%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20been%20designated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dea.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-03%2FDEA_GOV_DIR-008-20%2520Fentanyl%2520Flow%2520in%2520the%2520United%2520States_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20the%20DEA%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20growing%20source%20of%20fentanyl%20precursors%2C%20with%20at%20least%20one%20documented%20case%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20working%20with%20a%20cartel%20to%20produce%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFentanyl%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dea.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-06%2FFentanyl-2020_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%20times%20stronger%20than%20heroin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20makes%2020%20times%20the%20profit%20of%20heroin%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%20%26quot%3BLow%20cost%2C%20high%20profit.%20There%20are%20just%20way%20too%20many%20profiting%20incentives%20for%20people%20to%20engage%20in%20these%20illicit%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Ross%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Boston%20College%2C%20said%20the%20Biden-Xi%20agreement%20in%20its%20current%20form%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarginal%20at%20best%20effect%26quot%3B%20on%20fentanyl%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocusing%20on%20China%20as%20the%20source%20of%20the%20problem%20has%20been%20because%20it's%20such%20an%20easy%20country%20to%20criticize%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20China%20is%20only%20one%20player%20in%20the%20fentanyl%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20has%20to%20solve%20its%20social%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20demand%20in%20America%20is%20there%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20international%20fentanyl%20supply%2C%20whether%20it's%20from%20Mexico%2C%20whether%20it's%20from%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESo%20why%20bother%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20at%20least%20signals%20an%20area%20on%20which%20Beijing%20and%20Washington%20can%20shake%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20Biden%20and%20Xi%20put%20their%20names%2C%20time%2C%20and%20effort%20behind%20the%20cause%20is%20a%20welcome%20head%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric%20Richardson%2C%20a%20law%20lecturer%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20consultancy%20INHR%2C%20which%20trains%20diplomats%20to%20work%20in%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20China%2C%20the%20fentanyl%20agreement%20%E2%80%94%20alongside%20other%20deals%20struck%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20like%20the%20reopening%20of%20a%20military%20hotline%20%E2%80%94%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20Beijing%20is%20open%20to%20playing%20ball%2C%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20trying%20to%20signal%20to%20Europe%20and%20other%20countries%20that%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20cooperate%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20the%20fentanyl%20deal%20has%20been%20an%20issue%20repeatedly%20pushed%20by%20US%20officials%2C%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20that's%20been%20critical%20for%20President%20Biden%20in%20the%20coming%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20also%20something%20that's%20not%20a%20high-cost%20item%20issue%20for%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20or%20China%20to%20agree%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20facet%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-11-14%2Fbiden-xi-to-announce-deal-for-fentanyl-crackdown-by-china%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fus-commerce-dept-removes-chinese-agency-entity-list-federal-register-2023-11-16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20involves%20the%20US%20to%20lifting%20sanctions%20on%20the%20Forensic%20Public%20Security%20Institute%2C%20a%20Chinese%20government%20agency%20that%20Washington%20has%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20Xinjiang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20China%20also%20stands%20to%20gain%20from%20the%20agreement%20by%20learning%20from%20America's%20counter-narcotics%20branches%2C%20so%20it%20may%20guard%20against%20a%20potential%20fentanyl%20crisis%20of%20its%20own%2C%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZha%2C%20from%20Peking%20University%2C%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20expertise%20in%20source-tracing%20a%20harmful%20substance%2C%20including%20that%20to%20a%20precursor%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BChina%20is%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20illicitly%20trade%20substances%20that%20harm%20its%20population%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-help-us-deal-fentanyl-problem-biden-xi-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700209981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655707d622cf74a5739918c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-help-us-deal-fentanyl-problem-biden-xi-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DEA%20says%20China%20is%20a%20primary%20source%20for%20fentanyl%20precursors%2C%20but%20experts%20told%20BI%20a%20crackdown%20by%20Beijing%20probably%20won't%20make%20a%20dent%20on%20US%20streets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40insider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-help-us-deal-fentanyl-problem-biden-xi-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market%20is%20edging%20toward%20extremes%20of%20Great%20Depression%20and%20dot-com%20eras%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225176%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20of%20a%20stock%20trader%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655605d54ca513d8242a61d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223882%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEquities%20are%20look%20historically%20high%20relative%20to%20government%20bonds.%3Cp%3EJohannes%20Eiselle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStock-market%20valuations%2C%20by%20one%20measure%2C%20have%20hit%20highs%20surpassed%20only%20a%20few%20times%20in%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEquities%20look%20historically%20high%20relative%20to%20government%20bonds%2C%20according%20to%20PIMCO%20and%20GAM%20Asset%20Management.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20market's%20upbeat%20expectations%20on%20future%20corporate%20earnings%20may%20%26quot%3Bface%20disappointment%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20PIMCO.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20rally%20that%20defied%20high%20interest%20rates%20and%20recession%20calls%2C%20stock%20valuations%20are%20now%20edging%20toward%20levels%20seen%20before%20some%20of%20the%20greatest%20market%20meltdowns%20in%20history%20%E2%80%93%20by%20one%20measure%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20time-tested%20way%20of%20assessing%20whether%20equities%20are%20fairly%20valued%20is%20by%20comparing%20them%20with%20government%20bonds%2C%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20forms%20of%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20by%20that%20metric%2C%20stocks%20are%20looking%20historically%20expensive%2C%20according%20to%20experts%20from%20PIMCO%20and%20GAM%20Asset%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20measure%20of%20the%20richness%20of%20stocks%20relative%20to%20debt%20is%20the%20so-called%20equity%20risk%20premium%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20extra%20return%20on%20shares%20over%20Treasury%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metric%20has%20plunged%20this%20year%2C%20indicating%20stretched%20stock%20valuations%2C%20toward%20levels%20seen%20during%20the%20Great%20Depression%20of%20the%201930s%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20of%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelving%20deeper%20into%20historical%20data%2C%20we%20find%20that%20in%20the%20past%20century%20there%20have%20been%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20instances%20when%20US%20equities%20have%20been%20more%20expensive%20relative%20to%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20during%20the%20Great%20Depression%20and%20the%20dot-com%20crash%2C%26quot%3B%20PIMCO%20portfolio%20managers%20Erin%20Browne%2C%20Geraldine%20Sundstrom%2C%20and%20Emmanuel%20Sharef%20write%20in%20a%20recent%20research%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20suggests%20equities%20likely%20won't%20stay%20this%20expensive%20relative%20to%20bonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20historically%20low%20equity%20risk%20premium%20is%20a%20deterrent%20to%20investing%20in%20stocks%2C%20according%20to%20Julian%20Howard%20of%20Switzerland's%20GAM%20Asset%20Management.%20It%20means%20stocks%20are%20offering%20investors%20little%20incentive%20to%20choose%20them%20over%20risk-free%20assets%20such%20as%20government%20debt%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20may%20turn%20away%20potential%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20equity%20risk%20premium%20is%20very%2C%20very%20narrow.%20Now%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20actually%20almost%20negative%2C%26quot%3B%20Howard%20said%20in%20comments%20on%20the%20GAM%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20because%20what%20it%20is%20saying%20is%20that%20actually%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20equities%20in%20the%20short%20to%20medium%20term%2C%20because%20if%20you%20invest%20in%20the%20six-month%20Treasury%20bill%2C%20which%20is%20giving%20you%205.5%25%20completely%20free%20of%20risk%2C%20then%20that's%20actually%20a%20risk-reward%20that%20is%20completely%20unbeatable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20stocks%20are%20on%20track%20for%20their%20best%20month%20in%20a%20year%20amid%20expectations%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20may%20have%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20its%20interest-rate%20increases%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20economy%20remains%20resilient%20and%20inflation%20has%20moderated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20up%207.4%25%20in%20November%2C%20taking%20its%20year-to-date%20gains%20to%2017.3%25%2C%20amid%20optimism%20that%20corporate%20earnings%20will%20remain%20buoyant%20in%20the%20coming%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20PIMCO%20cautions%20against%20that%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20that%20robust%20forward%20earnings%20expectations%20might%20face%20disappointment%20in%20a%20slowing%20economy%2C%20which%2C%20coupled%20with%20elevated%20valuations%20in%20substantial%20parts%20of%20the%20markets%2C%20warrants%20a%20cautious%20neutral%20stance%20on%20equities%2C%20favoring%20quality%20and%20relative%20value%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Browne%2C%20Sundstrom%2C%20and%20Sharef%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-valuations-near-great-depression-dot-com-extremes-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700209851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6556060536d588dc55d1580e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-valuations-near-great-depression-dot-com-extremes-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock-market%20valuations%2C%20by%20one%20measure%2C%20have%20hit%20levels%20surpassed%20only%20a%20few%20times%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20the%20Great%20Depression%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bubble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22avarma%40insider.com%20(Anil%20Varma)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-valuations-near-great-depression-dot-com-extremes-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Philippines%20hit%20by%20undersea%20earthquake%20of%20up%20to%207.2%20magnitude%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%