will%20adopt%20RCS%20messaging%2C%20a%20step%20Google%20has%20been%20urging%20them%20to%20take%20for%20years.%20RCS%2C%20or%20Rich%20Communications%20Services%2C%20is%20an%20advanced%20messaging%20protocol%20that%20offers%20features%20such%20as%20read%20receipts%2C%20typing%20indicators%2C%20high-resolution%20media%20sharing%2C%20and%20group%20chats.%20This%20move%20will%20provide%20a%20better%20messaging%20experience%20for%20both%20Android%20and%20iPhone%20users%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20enjoy%20enhanced%20messaging%20without%20the%20need%20for%20third-party%20apps%20like%20WhatsApp.%20Apple's%20support%20for%20RCS%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20next%20year%2C%20potentially%20with%20the%20release%20of%20iOS%2018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fexplained-what-is-rcs-messaging-what-it-means-for-iphone-users-android-users-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F105282958.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Key%20Role%20Of%20Kim%20Jong%20Un's%2010-Year-Old%20Daughter%20In%20North%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20a%20school-age%20girl%20in%20a%20puffy%20white%20winter%20coat%20held%20her%20father's%20hand%20to%20stroll%20past%20a%20weapon%20designed%20to%20obliterate%20an%20American%20city%2C%20and%20set%20a%20new%20course%20for%20North%20Korea's%20propaganda%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%2C%20who%20made%20her%20debut%20at%20the%20test%20of%20an%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20designed%20to%20deliver%20a%20nuclear%20warhead%20to%20the%20US%20mainland.%20No%20other%20child%20of%20a%20North%20Korean%20leader%20had%20ever%20been%20shown%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20at%20such%20an%20early%20age%2C%20and%20her%20appearance%20broke%20the%20tradition%20of%20keeping%20the%20leader's%20children%20out%20of%20the%20public's%20eye%20until%20they%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20state's%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20been%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Brespected%20daughter%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbeloved%20child%26quot%3B%20by%20state%20media%2C%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20reveal%20her%20actual%20name%20-%20thought%20to%20be%20Ju%20Ae.%20South%20Korea's%20spy%20agency%20has%20pegged%20her%20age%20at%20about%2010%20and%20believes%20her%20to%20be%20the%20second%20of%20three%20children%20between%20Kim%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Ri%20Sol%20Ju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20Kim's%20daughter%20in%20state%20propaganda%20appears%20to%20be%20showing%20the%20public%20there%20is%20another%20generation%20waiting%20to%20run%20the%20family%20dynasty%20forged%20in%20the%20Cold%20War%20and%20it%20will%20rely%20on%20nuclear%20weapons%20for%20its%20survival.%20She%20humanizes%20Kim%20as%20a%20father%2C%20with%20the%20possible%20intent%20of%20conveying%20a%20message%20to%20North%20Korean%20parents%20that%20supporting%20an%20arms%20program%20means%20protecting%20their%20children%20from%20a%20US%20invasion%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bunique%26quot%3B%20socialist%20state%20forged%20by%20the%20Kim%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20preservation%20of%20the%20Kim%20family%20rule%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20inextricably%20tied%20to%20the%20country's%20weapons%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soo%20Kim%2C%20a%20former%20Korea%20analyst%20at%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%2C%20who%20now%20works%20at%20US-based%20management%20consulting%20firm%20LMI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20while%20the%20intent%20may%20be%20to%20soften%20the%20image%20of%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%2C%20that%20could%20be%20a%20hard-sell.%20%26quot%3BThe%20North%20Korean%20people%20are%20still%20starving%20and%20living%20under%20draconian%20repression%20-%20missiles%20or%20not.%20And%20unless%20Kim%20takes%20dramatic%20steps%20to%20improve%20the%20living%20conditions%20of%20his%20people%20and%20give%20them%20true%20freedom%2C%20their%20perceptions%20of%20Kim%20are%20unlikely%20to%20change%20fundamentally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20has%20not%20stopped%20North%20Korea%20from%20using%20the%20daughter%20for%20political%20purposes.%20She%20has%20appeared%2016%20times%20in%20public%20over%20the%20past%20year%20-%20with%2013%20of%20the%20events%20related%20to%20the%20military%2C%20two%20for%20sports%20and%20one%20for%20the%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20information%20from%20the%20South%20Korean%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20more%20than%20a%20week%20after%20her%20debut%2C%20the%20daughter%20was%20by%20her%20father's%20side%20again.%20She%20looked%20a%20bit%20more%20polished%20in%20a%20long%20black%20coat%20that%20was%20the%20same%20color%20as%20Kim%20Jong%20Un's%20for%20a%20photo%20session%20to%20celebrate%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20powerful%20ballistic%20missile%20-%20prompting%20%26quot%3Bstormy%20cheers%20of%20'Hurrah!'%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20Korean%20Central%20News%20Agency%20dispatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20biggest%20moment%20on%20the%20public%20stage%20in%20North%20Korea%20likely%20took%20place%20in%20February%2C%20when%20she%20joined%20her%20mother%20and%20father%20at%20a%20banquet%20honoring%20the%20military%20and%20was%20placed%20front%20and%20center%20in%20a%20photo%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20members%20of%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20joined%20her%20father%20at%20a%20military%20parade%20where%20his%20regime%20rolled%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20Pyongyang%20its%20biggest%20display%20of%20missile%20designed%20to%20deliver%20nuclear%20strikes%20on%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Brespected%20daughter%26quot%3B%20entered%20on%20her%20father's%20arm%20as%20soldiers%20applauded.%20She%20was%20then%20perched%20in%20a%20seat%20of%20honor%20to%20see%20festivities%20that%20included%20skydivers%20in%20neon%20lights%20descending%20to%20the%20grounds%20and%20thousands%20of%20goose-stepping%20military%20personnel%20shouting%20praise%20to%20Kim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20display%20of%20the%20weapons%20and%20his%20daughter%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20the%20world%20that%20North%20Korea%20won't%20be%20bargaining%20away%20its%20nuclear%20arsenal%20any%20time%20soon.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20personal%20touch%20about%20the%20importance%20to%20the%20Kim%20regime%2C%20when%20the%20daughter%20joined%20her%20father%20during%20the%20display%20and%20gently%20brushed%20his%20cheeks%20-%20in%20front%20of%20the%20fawning%20eyes%20of%20state%20media%2C%20which%20captured%20the%20moment%20and%20broadcast%20it%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20since%20been%20a%20staple%20at%20tests%20of%20new%20weapons%2C%20sat%20by%20her%20father's%20side%20as%20he%20smoked%20cigarettes%20at%20the%20country's%20new%20space%20agency%20and%20watched%20soccer%20matches%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20raised%20speculation%20on%20whether%20she%20will%20be%20named%20successor.%20Given%20her%20young%20age%20and%20opaque%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20leadership%20works%2C%20it%20is%20probably%20too%20early%20to%20tell%20if%20she%20has%20been%20chosen%20to%20take%20over.%20South%20Korea's%20National%20Intelligence%20Service%20believes%20there's%20an%20older%20brother%20yet%20to%20be%20displayed%20a%20public%20event.%20The%20brother%20would%20be%20the%20preferred%20choice%20under%20North%20Korea's%20patriarchal%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20Kim%20would%20install%20his%20elementary%20school-age%20daughter%20in%20a%20government%20role%20now%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20all%20but%20assure%20her%20of%20official%20status.%20Given%20Kim's%20relatively%20young%20age%20of%2039%2C%20he%20could%20be%20in%20power%20for%20decades.%20Still%2C%20he's%20overweight%20and%20a%20heavy%20smoker%20who%20has%20battled%20health%20problems%2C%20so%20succession%20is%20a%20subject%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20propaganda%20is%20expected%20to%20keep%20her%20in%20a%20prominent%20role.%20North%20Korea%20issued%20stamps%20with%20photos%20from%20public%20debut%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bnoble%20child%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20ICBM%20launch%20and%20Saturday%20will%20mark%20the%20one-year%20anniversary%20of%20the%20launch%20with%20its%20first%20ever%20Day%20of%20Missile%20Industry%2C%20which%20shows%20its%20%26quot%3Bmight%20as%20a%20world-class%20nuclear%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700203980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhbgetrjo_kim-jong-un-daughter_625x300_17_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-uns-daughter-marks-a-year-as-countrys-propaganda-star-4581626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20year%20ago%2C%20a%20school-age%20girl%20in%20a%20puffy%20white%20winter%20coat%20held%20her%20father's%20hand%20to%20stroll%20past%20a%20weapon%20designed%20to%20obliterate%20an%20American%20city%2C%20and%20set%20a%20new%20course%20for%20North%20Korea's%20propaganda%20apparatus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-uns-daughter-marks-a-year-as-countrys-propaganda-star-4581626%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-uns-daughter-marks-a-year-as-countrys-propaganda-star-4581626%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-uns-daughter-marks-a-year-as-countrys-propaganda-star-4581626%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20battle%20for%20Gaza%20rages%2C%20hostage%20families%20wait%20with%20trepidation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700203674000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105282855%2Cimgsize-94590.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbring-them-home-as-the-battle-for-gaza-rages-hostage-families-wait-with-trepidation%2Farticleshow%2F105282789.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105282789.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbring-them-home-as-the-battle-for-gaza-rages-hostage-families-wait-with-trepidation%2Farticleshow%2F105282789.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbring-them-home-as-the-battle-for-gaza-rages-hostage-families-wait-with-trepidation%2Famp_articleshow%2F105282789.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbring-them-home-as-the-battle-for-gaza-rages-hostage-families-wait-with-trepidation%2Famp_articleshow%2F105282789.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mind%20the%20Gap%3A%20A%20Slender%20Upper%20and%20a%20Heavy%20Lower%20Arm%20Define%20India%E2%80%99s%20K-Shaped%20Trajectory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F13092208%2FIMG_2134-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dissonance%20on%20whether%20India%20is%20indeed%20growing%20as%20strongly%20as%20the%20reported%20GDP%20numbers%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20remains%20unsettled%20with%20new%20evidence%20pointing%20towards%20a%20hugely%20distorted%20K-shaped%20trend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20true%20test%20of%20economic%20growth%20lies%20in%20its%20relevance%20for%20households%20(HH)%2C%20whose%20income%20in%20the%20Indian%20context%20represents%2076%25%20of%20GDP.%20The%20key%20GDP%20growth%20drivers%20in%20recent%20times%20have%20been%20the%20large%20government%20capex%20(7%25%20of%20total%20spending)%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20growing%20over%2060%25%20year-over-year%2C%20and%20the%20strong%20pace%20of%20leveraged%20consumption.%20However%2C%20the%20endogenous%20growth%20components%20exhibit%20structural%20feebleness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFirst%2C%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20data%20(August%202023)%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eproject%20approvals%20by%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%3Cspan%3E%20revealed%20the%20shallowness%20of%20the%20claimed%20private%20capex%20revival.%20While%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20projects%20sanctioned%20by%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%20increased%20by%2014.9%25%20on%20three%20year%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20(CAGR)%20till%20FY23%20at%20Rs%202.7%20trillion%2C%20it%20is%20majorly%20concentrated%20in%20the%20non-industrial%20sector%2C%20i.e.%20the%20infrastructure%20sector%20(Rs%201.6%20trillion)%2C%20mainly%20roads%2C%20dependent%20on%20government%20capex.%20Total%20project%20cost%20excluding%20Infra%20and%20metals%20at%20Rs%20632%20billion%20saw%20a%20contraction%20of%201.6%25%20on%20three-year%20CAGR.%20The%20implied%20lack%20of%20manufacturing%20sector%20jobs%20is%20now%20corroborated%20in%20the%20latest%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20survey%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20(October%2C%202023).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESecond%2C%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%2019%25%20year-over-year%20decline%20in%20net%20financial%20savings%20of%20households%20in%20FY19%20(RBI)%20was%20glossed%20over%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20rising%20household%20confidence%20with%20respect%20to%20their%20current%20and%20future%20incomes%2C%20a%20la%20Tobin%E2%80%99s%20wealth%20effect%20(1967).%20Accordingly%2C%20expectations%20of%20higher%20income%20growth%20should%20reduce%20the%20current%20saving%20rate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20facts%20are%20leaning%20towards%20Modigliani%E2%80%99s%20life%20cycle%20hypothesis%20(1955).%20A%20deceleration%20or%20decline%20in%20the%20real%20income%20of%20workers%20(who%20save)%20relative%20to%20those%20of%20retirees%20(who%20dis-save)%2C%20would%20reinforce%20the%20decline%20in%20savings%20as%20consumption%20for%20the%20saving%20cohorts%20gets%20adjusted%20slower%20than%20the%20erosion%20in%20real%20incomes%2C%20thereby%20catalysing%20leveraged%20spending.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20empirical%20estimates%20for%20FY08-FY19%3Cspan%3E%20show%20that%20a%201%20percentage%20point%20decline%20in%20real%20income%20would%20imply%20a%20lesser%20(0.6%20percentage%20point)%20decline%20in%20consumption%20thereby%20resulting%20in%20a%20decline%20in%20HH%20savings%20(-0.3%20percentage%20points).%20These%20estimates%20imply%20that%20the%20contraction%20in%20HH%20savings%20and%20the%20decline%20in%20savings%20rate%20since%20FY12%20is%20due%20to%20slowing%20or%20declining%20incomes%20rather%20than%20bountiful%20incomes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20the%20combination%20of%20actual%20net%20financial%20savings%20of%20RBI%20data%20(-18.8%25%20year-over-year%20in%20FY23)%2C%20an%20estimated%206.2%25%20growth%20in%20physical%20savings%2C%20and%20a%2012.5%25%20decline%20in%20investments%20in%20gold%20and%20silver%20(trade%20data)%2C%20the%20overall%20savings%20for%20HH%20in%20FY23E%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20contracted%20by%203.7%25%20year-over-year%20in%20FY23E.%20Adding%20household%20savings%20to%20private%20final%20consumption%20expenditure%20we%20get%20household%20incomes%2C%20which%20in%20real%20terms%20grew%20at%203.1%25%20in%20FY23%20and%202.8%25%20on%20a%20four-year%20CAGR%20converting%20into%20real%20per-capita%20income%20growth%20of%201.7%25%20per%20capita%20basis%2C%20ie.%20lowest%20in%2040%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20net-worth%20effect%20from%20the%20rise%20in%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20has%20little%20impact%20on%20HH%20spending.%20And%20while%20government%20capex%20has%20a%20marginal%20positive%20impact%20on%20HH%20spending%2C%20it%20depresses%20HH%20savings%20significantly.%20The%20impact%20of%20higher%20real%20interest%20rates%20along%20with%20higher%20tax%20incidence%20from%20higher%20government%20capex%20is%20seen%20having%20a%20crowding%20out%20effect%2C%20rather%20than%20crowding%20in%20effect%2C%20as%20is%20commonly%20believed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThird%2C%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20latest%20annual%20periodic%20labor%20force%20survey%20(PLFS)%202022-23%20reported%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20estimated%20unemployment%20rate%20falling%20to%20a%205-year%20low%20at%203.4%25%2C%20-1%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year.%C2%A0%20There%20is%20also%20a%20concomitant%20rise%20in%20the%20rate%20of%20people%20participating%20in%20the%20labour%20force%20(42.4%25%2C%20%2B1.1%20percentage%20points%20YoY%2C%20all%20age%20groups)%20and%20worker-population%20ratio%20(41.1%25%2C%20%2B1.5%20percentage%20points).%20However%2C%20the%20composition%20of%20these%20variables%20reflects%20the%20employment%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findia-economic-growth-covid-19-rbi-shaktikanta-das%5C%22%3EFrom%20V-Shaped%20to%20K-Shaped%2C%20Understanding%20the%20Alphabet%20Soup%20of%20Projected%20Indian%20Growth%20Recovery%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rise%20in%20worker%20population%20ratio%20(1.5%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year)%2C%20representing%20the%20employment%20rate%2C%20is%20significantly%20led%20by%20rural%20(%2B1.5%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year)%2C%20mainly%20the%20rural%20young%20cohorts%20with%20(%2B4.3%20percentage%20points)%20and%20a%20contrasting%20trend%20of%20a%20decline%20in%20mature%20rural%20males%20(30%2B%20years).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%20rural%20males%20working%20in%20agriculture%20and%20services%2C%20and%20a%20rise%20in%20rural%20construction.%20Females%20have%20moved%20into%20agriculture%20both%20in%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas.%20Work%20in%20the%20overall%20better-paying%20urban%20areas%20has%20contracted%2C%20while%20it%20has%20expanded%20in%20lesser-paying%20agriculture%20and%20rural%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%201.5%20percentage%20points%20increased%20proportion%20of%20self-employment%20(57.3%25)%20which%20is%20the%20residual%20impact%20of%20contractions%20in%20regular%20and%20casual%20work%20particularly%20in%20the%20manufacturing%2C%20urban%20construction%2C%20and%20services%20sectors%20along%20with%20a%20substantial%20decline%20in%20casual%20work%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccounting%20for%20the%20rise%20in%20%E2%80%98helper%20in%20household%20enterprise%E2%80%99%2C%20represented%20by%20forced%20self-employment%20in%20rural%20areas%20(largely%20unpaid%20labour)%2C%20the%20estimated%20effective%20unemployment%20rate%20has%20risen%20by%200.32%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year%20to%2025.4%25%20in%20FY23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proportion%20of%20workers%20engaged%20in%20agriculture%20rose%20again%20to%2045.8%25%20in%20FY23%20(%2B0.3%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year)%20versus%2044%25%20in%20FY18.%20The%20share%20for%20industry%2C%20including%20manufacturing%2C%20declined%200.2%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year%20to%2012.3%25%20and%20so%20did%20the%20share%20for%20services%20(-0.7%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year%20to%2027.8%25).%20Net%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20rural%20and%20decline%20in%20urban%20construction%2C%20the%20share%20of%20workers%20in%20construction%20increased%20to%2013%25%20%2B0.6%20percentage%20points%20year-over-year).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAggregating%20the%20incomes%20from%20regular%20(Rs%2020%2C039%20per%20month%2C%2021%25%20of%20workers)%2C%20casual%20(Rs%208%2C547%2C%2022%25)%2C%20and%20self-employment%20work%20(Rs%2013%2C347%2C%2057%25)%20average%20per%20worker%20income%20based%20on%20PLFS%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2013%2C467%20per%20month%20in%20FY23%20or%205.9%25%20four-year%20CAGR%2C%20translating%20into%200%25%20growth%20in%20real%20terms%20(net%20of%20inflation).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20estimated%201QFY24%20real%20earnings%20growth%20remained%20low%20at%202.9%25%20year-over-year%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20real%20private%20final%20consumption%20expenditure%20growth%20of%206%25%20in%201QFY24%20as%20per%20GDP%20data.%20Thus%2C%20there%20is%20a%20flagrant%20disconnect%20between%20the%20household%20situation%20as%20per%20the%20PLFS%20and%20the%20strong%20real%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EExhibit%201%3A%20Overall%20worker%20earnings%3A%20Regular%2C%20casual%20and%20self-employed%20(4-year%20CAGR%2C%20%25)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115645%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.56.29%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115645%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.56.29%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115645%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.56.29%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x183.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115645%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.56.29%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x624.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-im