20nine%20cities%20to%20demand%20climate%20action%2C%20backed%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bsick%20note%26quot%3B%20from%20climate%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67447253%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67447253.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67447253.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nimisha%20Priya%3A%20All%20About%20Indian%20Nurse%20Sentenced%20To%20Death%20In%20Yemen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYemen's%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20rejected%20the%20appeal%20against%20the%20death%20sentence%20of%20Indian%20nurse%20Nimisha%20Priya%2C%20who%20has%20been%20serving%20a%20prison%20sentence%20since%202017%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Yemeni%20national.%20Priya%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20killing%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi.%20She%20was%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Yemen%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi%20in%202018%20and%20her%20family%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20her%20release%20since%20then.%20With%20Yemini%20Supreme%20Court%20rejecting%20her%20appeal%2C%20it's%20now%20up%20to%20the%20country's%20President%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinistry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20Indian%20government%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20is%20providing%20consular%20assistance%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Nimisha%20Priya%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20from%20Palakkad%20district%20in%20Kerala.%20After%20completing%20a%20nursing%20training%20programme%2C%20she%20went%20to%20Yemen%20and%20worked%20in%20a%20few%20private%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Priya%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi%20in%202014%2C%20who%20promised%20to%20help%20her%20in%20starting%20her%20own%20clinic.%20A%20partnership%20was%20required%20since%20according%20to%20Yemeni%20law%2C%20partnering%20with%20a%20local%20is%20mandatory%20for%20starting%20any%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20partnership%20soon%20ended%20because%20of%20differences%20between%20Ms%20Priya%20and%20Mr%20Mahdi.%20She%20went%20ahead%20and%20started%20her%20clinic%20with%20him%20in%202015%2C%20but%20according%20to%20local%20outlets%2C%20Mahdi%20started%20threatening%20Ms%20Priya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahdi%20even%20took%20away%20her%20passport%20to%20ensure%20she%20doesn't%20leave%20Yemen.%20Ms%20Priya%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Mahdi%20due%20to%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%202016.%20But%20after%20his%20release%2C%20he%20continued%20giving%20troubles%20to%20Ms%20Priya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202017%2C%20she%20injected%20him%20with%20sedatives%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20retrieve%20her%20passport%20from%20his%20possession.%20However%2C%20he%20died%20of%20an%20overdose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Priya%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20murder%20in%202018%20and%20sent%20to%20jail.%20She%20was%20later%20sentenced%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20her%20family%20is%20doing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENimisha%20Priya's%20family%20has%20been%20fighting%20to%20get%20her%20justice%20since%202018.%20Her%20mother%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20seeking%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Yemen%20in%20spite%20of%20a%20travel%20ban%20for%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20negotiate%20the%20%26quot%3Bblood%20money%26quot%3B%20to%20save%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlood%20money%20refers%20to%20the%20compensation%20paid%20by%20an%20offender%20or%20his%20family%20to%20the%20victim%20or%20their%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Centre's%20lawyer%20said%20according%20to%20a%20notification%20issued%20recently%2C%20the%20travel%20ban%20may%20be%20relaxed%20and%20Indian%20nationals%20may%20be%20allowed%20to%20travel%20to%20Yemen%20for%20specific%20reasons%20and%20durations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20direct%20the%20Centre%20to%20negotiate%20the%20payment%20of%20blood%20money%20to%20save%20the%20woman%2C%20but%20asked%20it%20to%20pursue%20the%20legal%20remedies%20against%20the%20conviction%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700203080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F20ts0aho_kerala-nurse-nimisha-priya-twitter-650_650x400_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fnimisha-priya-all-about-indian-nurse-sentenced-to-death-in-yemen-4581645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nimisha%20Priya%20is%20from%20Palakkad%20district%20in%20Kerala.%20After%20completing%20a%20nursing%20training%20programme%2C%20she%20went%20to%20Yemen%20and%20worked%20in%20a%20few%20private%20hospitals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fnimisha-priya-all-about-indian-nurse-sentenced-to-death-in-yemen-4581645%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fnimisha-priya-all-about-indian-nurse-sentenced-to-death-in-yemen-4581645%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fnimisha-priya-all-about-indian-nurse-sentenced-to-death-in-yemen-4581645%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lily%20Gladstone%20Tears%20Up%20Describing%20the%20%E2%80%98Epidemic%E2%80%99%20of%20Missing%2C%20Murdered%20Indigenous%20Women%20and%20Children%20and%20the%20Fight%20for%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700202800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F1797956119.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C15px%252C5000px%252C2812px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235793306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lily%20Gladstone%20teared%20up