0parliament%20for%20another%20term%20as%20prime%20minister%20on%20Thursday%2C%20ending%20months%20of%20political%20deadlock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20despite%20divisions%20in%20the%20country%20over%20his%20decision%20to%20grant%20Catalan%20separatists%20amnesty%20in%20exchange%20for%20their%20crucial%20support%20in%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20political%20situation%20in%20Spain%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%E2%80%99s%20Socialist%20Party%20(PSOE)%20finished%20second%20in%20an%20inconclusive%20general%20election%20in%20July%2C%20but%20he%20has%20reached%20deals%20with%20six%20smaller%20parties%20to%20ensure%20the%20support%20of%20179%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20three%20more%20than%20the%20required%20absolute%20majority%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reestablish%20his%20minority%20coalition%20government%20with%20the%20far-left%20Sumar%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20smaller%20parties%20who%20have%20lent%20their%20support%20to%20Sanchez%20are%20two%20key%20Catalan%20separatist%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20return%2C%20Sanchez%20has%20agreed%20to%20grant%20amnesty%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20facing%20legal%20action%20for%20their%20role%20in%20Catalonia%E2%80%99s%20separatist%20movement%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20is%20Carles%20Puigdemont%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20regional%20government%20of%20Catalonia%20when%20it%20staged%20a%20failed%20secession%20bid%20in%202017%2C%20and%20who%20then%20fled%20to%20Belgium%20to%20avoid%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%3A%20%E2%80%98A%20united%20Spain%20is%20a%20better%20Spain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20defended%20the%20amnesty%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20two-day%20parliamentary%20debate%2C%20arguing%20it%20was%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cheal%20the%20wounds%E2%80%9D%20opened%20by%20the%20wealthy%20northeastern%20region%E2%80%99s%20independence%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20guarantee%20the%20unity%20of%20Spain%20through%20dialogue%20and%20forgiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2051-year-old%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Catalonia%20and%20other%20regions%20there%20are%20citizens%20who%20believe%20that%20they%20would%20be%20better%20going%20their%20own%20way.%20This%20government%20believes%20that%20a%20united%20Spain%20is%20a%20better%20Spain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20world%20leaders%20to%20congratulate%20Sanchez%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20good%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20side%20by%20side.%20We%20see%20many%20challenges%20in%20the%20world%20from%20a%20very%20similar%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%98political%20corruption%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20critics%20have%20accused%20Sanchez%20of%20trampling%20on%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20selling%20out%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdopting%20measures%20that%20go%20against%20the%20general%20interest%20in%20exchange%20of%20personal%20benefit%20is%20political%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20conservative%20Popular%20Party%20(PP)%2C%20Alberto%20Nunez%20Feijoo%2C%20said%20during%20the%20debate%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeijoo%20won%20the%20most%20seats%20in%20the%20election%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20secure%20enough%20support%20from%20other%20parties%20in%20his%20own%20bid%20to%20for%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20far-right%20Vox%20party%2C%20Santiago%20Abascal%2C%20went%20even%20further%2C%20calling%20the%20amnesty%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccoup%20d%E2%80%99etat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20vote%2C%20Feijoo%20walked%20across%20the%20chamber%20to%20shake%20Sanchez%E2%80%99s%20hand%20as%20leftist%20law