lance%20minister%20Atishi%20yesterday%20(Thursday%2C%20November%2017)%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20possible%20conflict%20of%20interest%20arising%20in%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20land%20acquisition%20case%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20in%20letters%20she%20has%20written%20to%20the%20directors%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecommending%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20south%20west%20Delhi%20district%20magistrate%2C%20Hemant%20Kumar%2C%20and%20division%20commissioner%2C%20Ashwani%20Kumar%2C%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20E-way%20land%20compensation%20award%20case%2C%20Atishi%20said%20has%20said%20this%20was%20a%20fit%20case%20for%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20chief%20secretary%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-chief-secretary-nhai-land-compensation%5C%22%3Edenied%3C%2Fa%3E%20any%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20land%20acquisition%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20forwarded%20a%20670%20page%20report%20prepared%20by%20the%20vigilance%20department%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20flagging%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20authority%20by%20the%20high-ranking%20officials%E2%80%9D%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%20Vinay%20Saxena.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20the%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20take%20cognizance%20of%20the%20vigilance%20report%20which%20is%20why%20the%20minister%20has%20forwarded%20it%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20agencies%20would%20act%20on%20source%20information%20and%20register%20a%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Delhi%20government%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20CBI%20flags%20this%20as%20a%20suitable%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%C2%A0%201988%2C%20the%20letter%20to%C2%A0%20the%20ED%20points%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9C93%25%20of%20payment%20of%20the%20land%20purchased%20by%20the%20beneficiaries%20may%20have%20been%20done%20in%20cash%E2%80%A6which%20might%20involve%20money%20laundering%20as%20well%20making%20it%20a%20case%20fit%20for%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20to%20the%20agencies%20said%20that%20as%20per%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20vigilance%20department%2C%20%E2%80%9Csince%20the%20land%20was%20purchased%20by%20the%20beneficiaries%20at%20only%207%25%20of%20the%20circle%20rate%20in%202015%2C%20there%20is%20a%20likelihood%20that%20the%20remaining%2093%25%20payment%20may%20have%20been%20done%20in%20cash.%20It%20appears%20that%20the%20exorbitant%20award%20of%20land%20compensation%20is%20not%20only%20a%20case%20of%20corruption%20but%20might%20involve%20money%20laundering%20as%20well%20making%20it%20a%20case%20fit%20for%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20minister%20writes%20in%20her%20letter%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20directed%20me%20to%20send%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20aforesaid%20preliminary%20report%20to%20you%20with%20a%20request%20that%20the%20case%20be%20registered%20by%20ED%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20alleged%20illegal%20transactions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20goes%20onto%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20examined%20the%20allegations%20based%20on%20the%20certified%20copies%20of%20the%20relevant%20files%20provided%20by%20the%20Special%20Secretary%20(Vigilance).%20No%20files%20whatsoever%20have%20been%20received%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20(Revenue)-cum-Divisional%20Commissioner%20despite%20asking%20for%20the%20same.%20Besides%2C%20I%20have%20also%20referred%20to%20publicly%20available%20documents%20related%20to%20land%20records%2C%20reports%2C%20and%20records%20available%20on%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%20I%20submitted%20the%20preliminary%20report%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%20on%2014.11.2023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20of%20the%20vigilance%20minister%20further%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20forwarded%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20preliminary%20report%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20for%20registering%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%201988%20and%20such%20other%20provisions%20of%20law%20as%20may%20be%20applicable%20in%20this%20case%20against%20Naresh%20Kumar%20(Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Delhi)%2C%20and%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20(Divisional%20Commissioner%2C%20Delhi)%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20DM%20South%20West%20Hemant%20Kumar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20CBI%20director%2C%20Atishi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Delhi%20has%20already%20referred%20certain%20aspects%20related%20to%20this%20case%20to%20CBI%3B%20particularly%2C%20the%20action%20of%20the%20then%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20South%20West%20Delhi%20in%20enhancing%20the%20land%20compensation%20exorbitantly.%20However%2C%20as%20you%20will%20find%20in%20this%20preliminary%20report%2C%20the%20then%20DM%20may%20just%20have%20executed%20the%20unlawful%20directions%20of%20his%20superiors.%20Therefore%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20then%20DM%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20Ashwani%20Kumar%2C%20Principal%20Revenue%20Secretary-cum-Divisional%20Commissioner)%20too%20should%20be%20investigated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20report%20says%20the%20enhanced%20compensation%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20850%20Cr%20and%20not%20Rs%20353%20crore%20as%20was%20initially%20presumed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20enhanced%20compensation%20for%20the%20claimants%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20award%20order%20passed%20by%20DM%20is%20Rs.%20856%20crore%20rupees%20and%20not%20Rs.%20311%20crore%20as%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20inquiry%20report%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20(DOV).%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20accepted%20this%20report%2C%20and%20did%20not%20raise%20any%20objections%20to%20the%20flawed%20approach%20adopted%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20(DOV)%20in%20its%20calculations%20thereby%20undercounting%C2%A0%20the%20extent%20of%20loss%20to%20the%20government%20exchequer.%20Further%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Shri%20Hemant%20Kumar%20is%20suspect%20and%20vigilance%20inquiry%2C%20prima-facie%2C%20raises%20serious%20questions%20on%20his%20financial%20propriety.%20A%20thorough%20investigation%20by%20the%20CBI%20will%20reveal%20the%20complete%20truth.%20However%2C%20this%20Rs%20856%20crore%20enhanced%20compensation%20is%20only%20a%20part%20of%20the%20story%20and%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20windfall%20gains%20can%20be%20calculated%20only%20after%20examination%20of%20how%20much%20they%20paid%20to%20purchase%20the%20land%20in%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20secretary%20has%20denied%20any%20wrong%20doing.%20He%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20week%2C%20%E2%80%9CCVO-cum-Chief%20Secretary%20took%20proactive%20action%20against%20the%20delinquent%20officer%20Sh.%20Hemant%20Kumar%20(IAS%2C%20AGMUT%202013)%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20he%20was%20firstly%20transferred%20out%20from%20Delhi%20to%20ANI%20(Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands)%20on%2019.10.2023%20and%20then%20was%20placed%20under%20suspension%20on%2020.10.2023.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20is%20also%20contesting%20any%20proposed%20extension%20in%20service%20of%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20secretary%20by%20the%20union%20government%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%20The%20chief%20secretary%20superannuates%20November%2030.%20The%20next%20date%20of%20hearing%20is%20November%2020.%20Notices%20have%20already%20been%20issued%20to%20the%20parties%20concerned%2C%20including%20the%20union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700195955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17100626%2FF-lTnQZW8AA_eoE.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-atishi-ed-cbi-chief-secretary-naresh-kumar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20comes%20shortly%20after%20CM%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20forwarded%20a%20vigilance%20report%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Delhi%20that%20takes%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20land%20overvaluation%20case%20where%20the%20chief%20secretary%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20having%20a%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-atishi-ed-cbi-chief-secretary-naresh-kumar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We've%20been%20calling%20Kim%20Jong%20Un's%20daughter%20by%20the%20wrong%20name%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20because%20of%20Dennis%20Rodman%2C%20Korean%20ex-spy%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kim%20Ju%20Ae%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20next%20to%20her%20father%20and%20mother.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e335e227e5db0018eeaadf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222819%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKim%20Jong%20Un's%20daughter%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20next%20to%20her%20father%20and%20mother.%3Cp%3EKCNA%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKim%20Jong%20Un's%20daughter%20has%20been%20known%20to%20the%20world%20as%20Kim%20Ju%20Ae%20since%20North%20Korea%20debuted%20her%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20a%20former%20South%20Korean%20spy%20veteran%20says%20her%20name%20is%20actually%20Kim%20Eun%20Ju%2C%20per%20The%20Korea%20Times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20the%20wrong%20name%20originated%20from%20a%20miscommunication%20Dennis%20Rodman%20had%20with%20Kim%20Jong%20Un.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20South%20Korean%20spy%20said%20the%20world%20has%20been%20giving%20the%20wrong%20name%20to%20daughter%20of%20North%20Korean%20dictator%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreatimes.co.kr%2Fwww%2Fnation%2F2023%2F11%2F103_363320.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520Kim%2527s%2520daughter%2527s%2520first%2520public%2Cand%2520the%2520third%2520in%25202017.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Korea%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20Choe%20Su%20Yong%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20Kim's%20daughter%20has%20been%20known%20as%20Kim%20Ju%20Ae%2C%20but%20that%20she's%20likely%20actually%20called%20Kim%20Eun%20Ju.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoe%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20counter-espionage%20division%20for%2020%20years%20at%20South%20Korea's%20National%20Intelligence%20Service%2C%20said%20the%20wrong%20name%20originated%20from%20former%20NBA%20star%20Dennis%20Rodman%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodman%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdennis-rodman-gave-kim-jong-un-trump-art-of-the-deal-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisited%20North%20Korea%20several%20times%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20a%20close%20friendship%20with%20Kim.%20Choe%20said%20that%20on%20one%20of%20his%20visits%2C%20the%20basketball%20legend%20had%20a%20miscommunication%20with%20Kim%20over%20the%20girl's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20Kim%20introduced%20his%20daughter%20to%20Rodman%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20North%20Korea%2C%20saying%20in%20Korean%20that%20'jeo-ae'%20is%20his%20daughter.%20Rodman%20seemed%20to%20have%20misunderstood%20the%20Korean%20word%20'jeo-ae'%20as%20her%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20Choe%20told%20The%20Times%2C%20citing%20sources%20in%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoe%20said%20Kim%20instead%20used%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bjeo-ae%26quot%3B%20to%20mean%20%26quot%3Bthat%20girl%26quot%3B%20in%20Korean%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodman%20had%20in%202013%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2013%2Fsep%2F09%2Fdennis-rodman-north-korea-baby-name%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Kim's%20daughter%20was%20named%20Ju%20Ae%2C%20saying%20he%20visited%20North%20Korea%20and%20held%20the%20girl%20in%20his%20arms%20when%20she%20was%20a%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Rodman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim's%20daughter%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fkim-ju-ae-north-korea-kim-jong-un-daughter-name-age%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicly%20debuted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20dictator%20in%20November%202022%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20that%20she%20could%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20his%20regime%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fkim-jong-un-daughter-meets-top-generals-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotentially%20become%20his%20successor.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20officials%20and%20intelligence%20services%20have%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2Fseouls-intelligence-reveals-new-facts-north-korean-leaders%2Fstory%3Fid%3D97677357%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eref