mer%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHina%20Jilani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Advocate%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Taskforce%20on%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEllen%20Johnson%20Sirleaf%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Liberia%20and%20Nobel%20Peace%20Laureate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERicardo%20Lagos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Chile%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuan%20Manuel%20Santos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Colombia%20and%20Nobel%20Peace%20Laureate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErnesto%20Zedillo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20letter%20is%20below.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20President%20Biden%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20a%20historic%20opportunity%20to%20help%20end%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20polarisation%20increases%2C%20the%20world%20needs%20you%20to%20set%20out%20a%20vision%20for%20peace.%20That%20vision%20must%20give%20hope%20to%20those%20who%20reject%20extremism%20and%20want%20the%20violence%20to%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20urge%20you%20to%20do%20two%20things%3A%20set%20out%20a%20serious%20peace%20plan%2C%20and%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%20to%20deliver%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20understand%20you%20want%20to%20help%20make%20Israelis%20safe.%20We%20share%20that%20objective%2C%20and%20have%20condemned%20the%20horrific%20Hamas%20attacks%20of%207%20October.%20We%20share%20too%20your%20commitment%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20self-determination.%20Palestinian%20and%20Israeli%20lives%20are%20of%20equal%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDestroying%20Gaza%20and%20killing%20civilians%20are%20not%20making%20Israelis%20safe.%20These%20actions%20will%20breed%20more%20terrorism%2C%20across%20the%20region%20and%20beyond.%20There%20is%20no%20military%20solution%20to%20this%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20is%20already%20feeding%20antisemitism%20and%20islamophobia%2C%20including%20in%20the%20USA.%20It%20undermines%20your%20other%20objectives%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20credibility%20and%20interests%20across%20the%20world%20are%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20policies%20of%20expanding%20illegal%20settlements%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20normalising%20relations%20with%20Arab%20countries%20while%20bypassing%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20have%20not%20made%20Israelis%20safe.%20Successive%20US%20governments%20have%20been%20complicit%20in%20these%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20make%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20safe%20is%20a%20lasting%20political%20solution.%20It%20must%20guarantee%20the%20security%20of%20Israel%2C%20whose%20people%20remain%20under%20threat.%20And%20it%20must%20meet%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20legitimate%20aspirations%20for%20their%20own%20state.%20Long%20denied%20during%2056%20years%20of%20occupation%2C%20these%20hopes%20are%20fading%20fast%2C%20as%20innocent%20Palestinians%20die%20in%20the%20rubble%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20stolen%20lands%20of%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20too%20long%20the%20world%20has%20spoken%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%20while%20allowing%20Israel%20to%20build%20a%20one-state%20reality.%20This%20has%20suited%20extremists%20in%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20who%20deny%20the%20other%20country%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20exist.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20end%20the%20empty%20rhetoric%2C%20and%20implement%20a%20serious%20peace%20plan%20that%20undermines%20extremists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plan%20should%20answer%20who%20runs%20Gaza%20next%2C%20end%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20accelerating%20annexation%20of%20Palestinian%20land%2C%20and%20address%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20security%20concerns.%20It%20must%20recognise%20the%20equal%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%2C%20and%20be%20rooted%20in%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20UN%20Charter%20and%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraelis%20and%20Palestinians%20will%20not%20end%20this%20conflict%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20history%20is%20too%20complicated%2C%20the%20politics%20too%20polarised%2C%20the%20compromises%20required%20too%20difficult.%20But%20peace%20cannot%20be%20imposed%20from%20outside.%20It%20requires%20bold%20leaders%20with%20legitimacy%20and%20credibility%20among%20their%20peoples%2C%20and%20a%20commitment%20to%20two%20states%20living%20together%20peacefully.%20Those%20leaders%20are%20not%20currently%20in%20power%20in%20Palestine%20or%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USA%20cannot%20bring%20peace%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20on%20its%20own.%20You%20can%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%2C%20including%20countries%20from%20the%20region%20and%20Europe%20who%20want%20a%20just%20settlement.%20This%20coalition%20can%20restore%20a%20political%20horizon%2C%20and%20rebuild%20the%20trust%20needed%20for%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgress%20will%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20or%20quick.%20Years%20of%20mistrust%20and%20violence%20have%20left%20the%20two%20peoples%20far%20from%20readiness%20to%20negotiate.%20A%20comprehensive%20agreement%20will%20take%20years.%20It%20will%20demand%20enormous%20political%20courage%20from%20all%20leaders%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20significant%20domestic%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20start.%20A%20serious%20peace%20plan%20is%20not%20a%20distraction%20from%20resolving%20the%20current%20crisis%3B%20it%20is%20a%20prerequisite.%20There%20is%20a%20slender%20opportunity%20to%20build%20on%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20UN%20Security%20Council%20Resolution.%20But%20progress%20is%20more%20likely%20if%20that%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20lasting%20peace%2C%20not%20just%20de-escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe-escalation%20is%20not%20enough.%20We%20cannot%20go%20back%20to%20managing%20the%20conflict.%20It%20will%20erupt%20again%20and%20again%20with%20more%20death%20and%20misery.%20The%20conflict%20must%20be%20resolved%2C%20permanently%2C%20through%20negotiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%2C%20you%20said%20last%20month%20that%20American%20leadership%20is%20what%20holds%20the%20world%20together.%20This%20conflict%20is%20tearing%20the%20world%20apart.%20We%20have%20spoken%20to%20Israelis%20whose%20families%20were%20murdered%20and%20taken%20hostage%2C%20and%20Gazans%20suffering%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%20We%20recognise%20their%20pain%2C%20anger%20and%20fear.%20We%20encourage%20you%20and%20Secretary%20Blinken%20to%20continue%20working%20to%20release%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20and%20end%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Elders%20learned%20from%20our%20founder%2C%20Nelson%20Mandela%2C%20that%20the%20road%20from%20hatred%20to%20forgiveness%20can%20be%20long%20and%20difficult.%20Some%20will%20never%20walk%20it.%20But%20the%20majority%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%20want%20to%20live%20in%20peace%2C%20not%20endure%20yet%20more%20violence.%20Please%20help%20them%20find%20the%20path%20to%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20will%20never%20forget%20your%20leadership%20if%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESigned%20by%20the%20Elders.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700194289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17093901%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-9.38.00.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-elders-joe-biden-israel-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Members%20of%20the%20organisation%20founded%20by%20Nelson%20Mandela%20told%20Biden%20that%20the%20US%20can%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%2C%20including%20countries%20from%20