5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63ecb893eeb52e0018869237%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChildren%20hold%20Ukrainian%20flags%20along%20the%20road%20near%20Sloviansk%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EYasuyoshi%20Chiba%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20the%20war%20began%2C%20thousands%20of%20Ukrainian%20children%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20their%20families.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20study%20found%20over%202%2C000%20of%20these%20children%20are%20now%20in%20Belarus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20Belarus%2C%20some%20children%20have%20been%20re-educated%20by%20nationalists%20and%20given%20military%20training.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20report%20from%20Yale%20University%20sheds%20new%20light%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20Ukrainian%20children%20who%20have%20been%20deported%20by%20Russia%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20the%20report%20says%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20military%20training%20and%20reeducation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Yale%20School%20of%20Public%20Health's%20Humanitarian%20Research%20Lab%2C%20which%20studied%20the%20deportation%20of%20thousands%20of%20Ukrainian%20children%2C%20found%20that%20the%20Russian%20and%20Belarusian%20governments%20have%20worked%20in%20tandem%20to%20organize%20such%20deportations.%20The%20report%20relied%20primarily%20on%20open-source%20research%20and%20some%20high-resolution%20satellite%20imagery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%202%2C442%20children%20from%20Ukraine%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20Belarus%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhub.conflictobservatory.org%2Fportal%2Fsharing%2Frest%2Fcontent%2Fitems%2Fb024b68ca6e54ecdadec2e79fa779f2d%2Fdata%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20two%20allied%20countries%20coordinated%20the%20transport%20of%20the%20children%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20six%20and%2017%20%E2%80%94%20from%20their%20home%20to%20a%20new%20life%20in%20Belarus%2C%20often%20by%20way%20of%20Russia%20first%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEight%20out%20of%2013%20facilities%20the%20children%20are%20taken%20to%20in%20Belarus%20include%20reeducation%20programs%20that%20serve%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20interests%20of%20Belarus'%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20instances%2C%20these%20programs%20include%20military%20training%2C%20according%20to%20Yale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20nine%20groups%20of%20children%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20reeducation%20programs%20and%20at%20least%20six%20groups%20of%20kids%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20endure%20some%20sort%20of%20military%20training%2C%20the%20report%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20at%20least%20two%20groups%20of%20children%20deported%20from%20Ukraine%20who%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20bases%20of%20the%20Internal%20Troops%20of%20Belarus%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20law%20enforcement%20force%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20The%20military%20unit%20has%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20violent%20suppression%20of%20pro-democracy%20protests%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelarusian%20troops%20have%20subjected%20Ukrainian%20children%20to%20military%20training%20that%20includes%20handling%20firearms%2C%20wearing%20body%20armor%2C%20and%20watching%20military%20parades%2C%20lectures%2C%20and%20combat%20demonstrations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20children%20have%20also%20been%20given%20medical%20treatment%20of%20an%20uncertain%20nature%2C%20called%20%26quot%3Brehabilitation%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Belarus%20government%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20hospital%20reported%20the%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20participate%20in%20%26quot%3Bexercise%20therapy%20classes%20and%20group%20psychological%20correction%2C%20massage%2C%20and%20halotherapy%2C%20water%20and%20electrotherapy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20a%20group%20of%2037%20Ukrainian%20children%20arrived%20in%20Belarus%20where%20they%20underwent%20unspecified%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20evaluations%26quot%3B%20during%20which%20they%20were%20also%20re-educated%2C%20the%20report%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-russia-has-abducted-more-than-13000-children-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeported%20Ukrainian%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20unknown.%20But%20official%20numbers%20from%20Ukraine%20suggest%20nearly%2020%2C000%20children%20have%20been%20deported%20or%20forcibly%20displaced%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F07%2F20%2Feurope%2Fbelarus-red-cross-ukraine-children-deportations-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20children's%20commissioner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Frussia-children-taken-ukraine%2F32527298.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaria%20Lvova-Belova%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20this%20summer%20that%20more%20than%20700%2C000%20Ukrainian%20children%20had%20been%20taken%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20Russia%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20those%20children%20came%20along%20with%20their%20parents%20and%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20in%20March%20issued%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Lvova-Belova%20on%20charges%20of%20illegally%20removing%20children%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20Russia%20since%20the%20war%20began.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20humanitarian%20law%20forbids%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-to-fast-track-adoption-of-deported-ukraine-orphans-kyiv-officials-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforcible%20transfer%20or%20deportation%3C%