20say%20they%20love%20life%20on%20the%20island%20and%20have%20plans%20to%20build%20another%20house%20next%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20vacations%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Findonesia-bali-tourist-mistake-travel-guide-local-tips-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Anna-Carina%20Tetzner%20and%20Sean%20Peel%20decided%20it%20was%20where%20they%20wanted%20to%20live%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20been%20based%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Australia%2C%20but%20always%20dreamt%20of%20living%20in%20Asia.%20After%20spending%20time%20in%20a%20few%20different%20countries%2C%20they%20realized%20they%20had%20left%20their%20heart%20in%20Bali%2C%20an%20island%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20experiencing%20the%20island%20as%20tourists%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we%20had%20been%20coming%20for%20three%20years%20in%20a%20row%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20house%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%2C%2039%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20their%20home%20in%20Bali.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554478f22cf74a573977d45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%20and%20Sean%20Peel%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20their%20modular%20home%20in%20Bali.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EFirst%20things%20first%3A%20Find%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%20the%20couple%20had%20friends%20on%20the%20island%2C%20who%20introduced%20them%20to%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20just%20outside%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-staying-at-a-tree-house-in-bali-for-cheap-2020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUbud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20town%20in%20central%20Bali%20that's%20known%20for%20its%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20rice%20terraces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20we%20loved%20it%2C%20and%20we%20signed%20the%20contract%20in%20early%202020%2C%20just%20before%20the%20pandemic%20broke%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exotiqproperty.com%2Fblog%2Fcan-foreigners-buy-property-in-bali%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrict%20property%20ownership%20laws%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Foreigners%20can't%20own%20land%2C%20but%20they%20can%20lease%20it%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20couple's%20case%2C%20they%20paid%20275%20million%20Indonesian%20Rupiah%2C%20or%20about%20%2417%2C000%2C%20for%20a%2020-year%20leasehold%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20empty%20plot%20of%20land.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655455794ca513d8242996c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20the%20couple's%20property%20is%20on%20a%20rice%20terrace%2C%20the%20ground%20had%20to%20be%20cleared%20and%20leveled%20before%20construction%20could%20commence.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20end%20of%20the%20initial%20lease%2C%20we%20get%20the%20right%20of%20first%20refusal%20to%20say%2C%20'Yes%2C%20we%20want%20to%20continue%20the%20lease%2C'%20or%20'No%2C%20we%20don't.'%20If%20we%20choose%20not%20to%2C%20then%20the%20actual%20land%2C%20and%20the%20house%20that%20we've%20built%20on%20it%2C%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20landowner%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%2C%2046%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20modular%20design%20for%20DIY%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20brick%20and%20mortar%2C%20the%20couple%20designed%20their%20own%20modular%20house%20that%20comprises%20steel%20frames%20and%20wood%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20main%20reason%20for%20going%20with%20a%20modular%20home%20was%20the%20limited%20access%20they%20had%20to%20the%20property%2C%20Peel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steel%20frames%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20house%20are%20being%20constructed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554559c4ca513d8242996c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20steel%20frames%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20house%20are%20being%20constructed.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20that%20leads%20to%20their%20home%20is%20narrow%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20anything%20larger%20than%20a%20small%20car%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20pass%20through.%20But%20with%20a%20modular%20design%2C%20parts%20of%20the%20house%20could%20be%20built%20offsite%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20steel%20fabricator%20making%20the%20panels%20for%20us.%20He'd%20put%20them%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20little%20pickup%2C%20drive%20them%20here%2C%20and%20we%20could%20just%20carry%20them%20to%20the%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20a%20modular%20design%20meant%20the%20couple%20could%20build%20the%20house%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20structure%20that's%20made%20out%20of%20components%20that%20they%20could%20just%20%26quot%3Bscrew%20together%26quot%3B%20would%20require%20less%20manpower%20than%20laying%20bricks%20conventionally%2C%20Peel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20building%20a%20frame%20for%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554491722cf74a573977d51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeel%20assembling%20the%20frame%20of%20their%20house.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20building%20method%20isn't%20all%20that%20common%20in%20Bali%2C%20Tetzner%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20of%20anyone%20who%20has%20built%20like%20us%2C%20pre-fabricated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20houses%20are%20built%20with%20Batako%2C%20a%20cheap%20sand%20and%20cement%20brick%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20all%20sorts%20of%20problems%2C%20including%20mold%20and%20moisture%20issues%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20that%20at%20all%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20modern%20homes%20in%20Bali%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbamboo-mansions-bali-photos-elora-hardy-ibuku-feature-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20using%20bamboo.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20data%20regarding%20modular%20homes%20in%20Bali%20could%20not%20be%20found%2C%20a%20Google%20search%20did%20result%20in%20multiple%20local%20construction%20companies%20specializing%20in%20building%20prefabricated%20structures.%20The%20designs%20found%20are%20not%20comparable%20to%20the%20couple's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22732%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20progress%20photo%20of%20the%20build.%20The%20exterior%20walls%20of%20the%20house%20have%20been%20partially%20installed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655455b94ca513d8242996ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20progress%20photo%20of%20the%20build.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPeel%20added%20that%20building%20his%20own%20house%20was%20always%20something%20that%20he%20had%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20was%20a%20builder%20and%20he%20had%20a%20hardware%20store%20back%20in%20Australia%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20tertiary-qualified%20mechanical%20engineer%2C%20and%20I've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20working%20with%20him%20doing%20renovations%20on%20houses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20renovated%20a%20house%20together%20before%2C%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bought%20and%20renovated%20an%20old%20apartment%20from%20the%201980s%20right%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Australia's%20Sunshine%20Coast%20in%202016%2C%20only%20six%20months%20after%20Sean%20and%20I%20met%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20where%20they%20lived%20before%20moving%20to%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20painting%20the%20wall%20green.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655449a24ca513d824299665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETetzner%20painting%20the%20walls%20of%20their%20home.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EAn%20open-plan%2C%20modern%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20of%20land%20measures%20about%206%2C500%20square%20feet%2C%20while%20the%20house%20takes%20up%20about%201%2C400%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20is%20made%20up%20of%20three%20rectangular%20buildings%20that%20are%20connected%20by%20two%20sheltered%20walkways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20building%20is%20where%20Tetzner's%20home%20pottery%20studio%20is%2C%20while%20the%20second%20comprises%20the%20kitchen%2C%20dining%2C%20and%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20building%20is%20where%20the%20couple's%20bedroom%20and%20bathroom%20are%20found%20%E2%80%94%20with%20an%20additional%20door%20leading%20to%20the%20garden%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home's%20dark%20gray%2C%20almost%20black%20steel-clad%20exterior%20cuts%20a%20striking%20figure%20amid%20the%20lush%20greenery%20surrounding%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20doors%20across%20the%20front%20of%20the%20house%2C%20creating%20an%20open%20floor%20plan%20that%20allows%20the%20island%20breeze%20to%20sweep%20through%20the%20interiors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20favorite%20spot%20is%20the%20second%20building%2C%20home%20to%20the%20shared%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20area%20is%20really%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20open%20to%20the%20jungle.%20We%20painted%20the%20house%20a%20very%20dark%20gray%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20black%20steel.%20So%20the%20contrast%20between%20that%2C%20the%20timber%2C%20and%20the%20green%20of%20the%20plants%20is%20quite%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple's%20home%20has%20an%20open%20layout.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554527522cf74a573977da0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple's%20home%20has%20an%20open%20layout.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20is%20also%20powered%20by%20the%20grid%20while%20water%20comes%20from%20a%20well%20that%20the%20couple%20installed%20on%20the%20property%2C%20Peel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWells%20are%20common%20in%20Ubud%2C%20where%20it%20rains%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%20While%20most%20people%20only%20drill%20their%20well%20around%2025%20meters%20deep%2C%20the%20couple's%20well%20is%2080%20meters%20into%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20that%20water%20for%20watering%20gardens%20and%20showering%2C%20and%20then%20we%20filter%20that%20water%20before%20drinking%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20started%20construction%20in%20December%202020%2C%20and%20the%20house%20was%20ready%20for%20them%20to%20move%20in%20by%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20they%20have%20been%20working%20on%20some%20final%20touches.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20a%20pool%2C%20which%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20Christmas%2C%20Peel%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilding%20during%20the%20wet%20season%20wasn't%20fun%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221045%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20walking%20along%20a%20walkway%20leading%20to%20the%20couple's%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65544dc04ca513d82429968b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeel%20walking%20along%20the%20walkway%20leading%20to%20the%20couple's%20home.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20the%20couple%20faced%20was%20that%20they%20started%20their%20project%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbali.com%2Fbali%2Fweather%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainy%20season%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20runs%20from%20November%20to%20March%2C%20and%20central%20areas%20like%20Ubud%20tend%20to%20be%20cooler%20and%20experience%20more%20rain%20than%20the%20coastal%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20kind%20of%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20gods%20in%20terms%20of%20when%20we%20could%20work%20and%20when%20we%20couldn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20we%20worked%20each%20day%20really%20depended%20upon%20the%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20all%2C%20Peel%20estimates%20that%20they%20worked%20between%2030%20to%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20building%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221109%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hallway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655455ca4ca513d8242996d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hallway.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20the%20two%20of%20them%20were%20also%20still%20new%20to%20the%20language%20and%20faced%20some%20communication%20barriers%20when%20liaising%20with%20local%20contractors%2C%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20languages%20spoken%20in%20Bali%20%E2%80%94%20Indonesian%20and%20Balinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20couple%20managed%20to%20get%20things%20done%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Google%20Translate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20deal%20with%20everybody%20here%20via%20WhatsApp%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20the%20Indonesians%2C%20or%20the%20Balinese%20do.%20All%20the%20businesses%20have%20WhatsApp%2C%20so%20you%20can%20just%20chat%20with%20them%20there%20and%20copy-paste%20your%20translated%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20feature%20isn't%20foolproof%20%E2%80%94%20leading%20to%20funny%20translations%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20it%20got%20the%20job%20done%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655455e636d588dc55d0894b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20open%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ELearning%20through%20the%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20lived%20nearby%20during%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20out%20living%20in%20a%20small%20resort%20that%20was%20about%20a%20five-minute%20scooter%20ride%20away%20from%20the%20site%20but%20then%20moved%20even%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20that%20it%20was%20getting%20annoying%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20motorbike%20every%20time%20we%20wanted%20to%20go%20home%20or%20eat%20something%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20then%20to%20rent%20a%20small%20house%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20the%20site%2C%20and%20that%20made%20a%20big%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221243%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area%20of%20the%20couple's%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65544b4922cf74a573977d6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area%20of%20the%20couple's%20home.%3Cp%3ESlow%20life%20in%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20originally%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20their%20own%20home%20had%20seemed%20daunting%2C%20the%20process%20wasn't%20as%20complicated%20as%20they%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20set%20your%20mind%20to%20it%2C%20you%20could%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Peel%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnna%20used%20to%20say%2C%20'How's%20this%20going%20to%20ever%20be%20finished%3F'%20And%20I%20would%20say%20to%20her%2C%20'It's%20just%20like%20eating%20an%20elephant.%20You%20do%20it%20one%20bite%20at%20a%20time.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221247%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple's%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6540b4b6284fe8aac522bb93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22831%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20took%20them%20a%20while%20to%20get%20used%20to%20the%20cultural%20differences%20in%20the%20way%20that%20the%20locals%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20in%20the%20Western%20world%20where%20you%20ask%20a%20tradesperson%20to%20be%20there%20at%20eight%20o'clock%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20that's%20exactly%20when%20they%20show%20up.%20Often%20if%20we%20did%20need%20a%20hand%20or%20a%20delivery%20or%20something%2C%20it's%20Bali%20time%20%E2%80%94%20they%20come%20whenever%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20really%20needed%20to%20be%20very%2C%20very%20patient%20and%20just%20allow%20things%20to%20kind%20of%20happen%20when%20they%20were%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20sin%20and%20shower%20are%20in%20the%20couple's%20open%20bathroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65544f2a36d588dc55d088ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ECapturing%20the%20moments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMidway%20through%20the%20project%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20documenting%20their%20progress%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40slowlifeinbali%2Fvideos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20weren't%20filming%20anything%20because%20we%20just%20didn't%20have%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20as%20time%20went%20on%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20little%20bit%20sad%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20the%20memories%2C%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20let%20me%20just%20see%20if%20I%20can%20put%20something%20very%20basic%20together%20that%20we%20could%20look%20back%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20on%20the%20couple's%20channel%20are%20both%20cinematic%20and%20raw%2C%20with%20stunning%20drone%20footage%20spliced%20together%20with%20scenes%20of%20the%20couple%20discussing%20their%20plans%20for%20the%20day%20and%20time-lapses%20of%20things%20getting%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDo%20your%20research%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65544bf636d588dc55d088c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cabinet%20in%20the%20couple's%20living%20room.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20piece%20of%20advice%20for%20others%20who%20want%20to%20build%20a%20home%20in%20Bali%3F%20Get%20at%20least%20three%20quotes%2C%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20impo