-ineffective-ukraine-war-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuch%20less%20significant%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdavidaxe%2F2023%2F09%2F03%2Fukraines-tb-2-drones-are-back-in-action-thats-an-ominous-sign-for-russia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econspicuous%20exceptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Russia%20made%20adjustments%20to%20its%20air%20defenses%20and%20electronic-warfare%20systems%20to%20counter%20them%20more%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20TB2%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20the%20word%20useless%2C%20but%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20find%20situations%20where%20to%20use%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Col.%20Volodymyr%20Valiukh%2C%20a%20commander%20in%20Ukraine's%20Main%20Intelligence%20Directorate%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Feurope%2F2023%2F10%2F31%2Fare-the-once-vaunted-bayraktar-drones-losing-their-shine-in-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20October%2026%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EBaykar's%20future%20projects%20in%20Ukraine%20do%20not%20hinge%20on%20the%20TB2%2C%20however.%20It%20also%20reportedly%20plans%20on%20constructing%20the%20newer%20Akinci%20drone%20at%20its%20plant%20in%20Ukraine.%20With%20sophisticated%20sensors%20and%20more%20hardpoints%20to%20carry%20heavier%20bombs%2C%20missiles%2C%20and%20even%20long-range%20standoff%20munitions%2C%20the%20Akinci%20is%20an%20entirely%20different%20beast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EDifferent%20military%20systems%20%26quot%3Bare%20designed%20for%20different%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20TB2%20was%20more%20visible%20during%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20this%20was%20when%20it%20was%20needed%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ali%20Bakir%2C%20a%20Turkey%20expert%20and%20non-resident%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Middle%20East%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221043%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayraktar%20Ukraine%20Zelenskyy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65562d9522cf74a573985b76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHaluk%20Bayraktar%2C%20center-left%2C%20signs%20a%20deal%20to%20build%20a%20drone%20maintenance%20and%20training%20center%20in%20Kyiv%20in%20September%202021.%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20Presidency%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIts%20mission%20was%20clear%3A%20disrupt%20Russian%20supply%20chains%20and%20stall%20the%20invasion%2C%20giving%20Ukraine%20the%20breathing%20room%20to%20regroup%20and%20rally%20Western%20military%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakir%20said%20of%20the%20TB2%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bachieved%20its%20intended%20mission%20efficiently%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EAs%20conflict%20has%20shifted%2C%20so%20too%20have%20Ukraine's%20%26quot%3Btactical%20requirements%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakir%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20TB2%20isn't%20as%20prominent%20now%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bits%20efficiency%20isn't%20in%20question%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Bstellar%20record%26quot%3B%20over%20various%20battlefields%20since%202020%20means%20%26quot%3Bmarket%20demand%20remains%20robust%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EJames%20Rogers%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-62962-20%26h%3D9412f7e5e68500052fc2b51d4713b6330d2851a57aa3d8aafc43aea2854e70f6%26postID%3D65562a6553ff61e69aa18bab%26postSlug%3Dturkish-firm-behind-bayraktar-tb2-drone-big-investment-in-ukraine-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPrecision-American-James-Patton-Rogers%252Fdp%252F1526125889%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%20and%20precision%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20agreed%20that%20the%20TB2's%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20utility%20and%20military%20effectiveness%26quot%3B%20had%20diminished%20in%20Ukraine%20but%20said%20Kyiv%20sees%20value%20in%20expanded%20cooperation%20with%20Baykar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20troops%20will%20still%20use%20the%20TB2%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20possible%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20adoption%2C%20and%20perhaps%20local%20production%2C%20of%20the%20Akinci%20%26quot%3Bwill%20aid%20Ukraine%20with%20its%20powerful%20sensors%20and%20standoff%20munitions%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Rogers%2C%20who%20is%20executive%20director%20at%20the%20Cornell%20Brooks%20School%20Tech%20Policy%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20Turkey%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20close%20long-term%2C%20strategic%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EBakir%20said%20defense%20collaboration%20between%20Kyiv%20and%20Ankara%2C%20which%20predates%20the%20current%20war%2C%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bforged%20over%20the%20years%20and%20solidified%20by%20recent%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20Bayraktar%20Akinci%20drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc45ec0f3dff001956d2e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBaykar's%20Bayraktar%20Akinci%20drone%20on%20display%20at%20Istanbul's%20Ataturk%20Airport%20in%20April.%3Cp%3EOguz%20Yeter%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBaykar's%20commitment%20to%20invest%20%24100%20million%20in%20three%20Ukrainian%20projects%20is%20a%20testament%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20to%20this%20enduring%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakir%20said.%