%2C%20the%20regiment%20set%20their%20camps%20on%20the%20bank.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20the%20British%20and%20put%20behind%20bars%20for%20over%20a%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20forced%20to%20retreat%20to%20Bangkok.%20While%20all%20the%20other%20women%20went%20back%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20%3Cem%3Edadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandma)%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20her%20father%2C%20who%20was%20out%20on%20a%20secret%20mission%2C%20was%20put%20in%20a%20Singapore%20jail.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20news%20of%20the%20atomic%20bombings%20in%20Japan%20surfaced%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%201945%2C%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20were%20bombed%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20the%20Japanese%20forces%20were%20forced%20to%20surrender.%20Two%20weeks%20later%2C%20on%2018%20August%201945%2C%20the%20plane%20carrying%20Netaji%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Tokyo%2C%20crashed.%20This%20came%20as%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20has%20jotted%20down%20her%20experiences%20from%20scraps%20of%20papers%20that%20have%20become%20a%20significant%20personal%20account%20of%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me